his dad was right. He hugged his friends and said goodbye.

"Thank you for coming to my party," he said. "I had a lot of fun."

"Sorry about the leak, Tom," his friends said. "We hope you have a better birthday next year."

Tom smiled. He was still happy. He had a good party and good friends. He had a lot of cake and presents. He decided to celebrate again when the leak was fixed. He knew his mom and dad loved him and would make him happy.

The end.
<|end|>


