Lily was a popular girl. She had many friends who liked to play with her. She liked to share her toys and make funny jokes. She was always happy and kind.

One day, Lily had a big sleepover at her house. She invited all her friends to come and have fun. They played games, sang songs, and ate yummy snacks. They had a lot of fun.

When it was time to go to bed, Lily showed her friends where they could sleep. She had a big bed with pink sheets and fluffy pillows. She said, "This is my bed. You can all seat on it and sleep with me. There is enough room for everyone."

Her friends were happy and thanked her. They all climbed on the bed and snuggled together. They said good night to each other and closed their eyes. Lily smiled and felt very lucky. She had the best friends and the best bed in the world. She fell asleep with a happy dream.
<|end|>


