Once upon a time, there was a little boy named Tim. Tim liked to play outside with his friends. One day, he went to the park to meet his best friend, Sam. They were very happy to see each other.

In the park, they found a big, dizzy merry-go-round. They took turns spinning it very fast. Tim and Sam laughed and laughed as they spun around. They felt dizzy, but they loved the feeling.

After playing on the merry-go-round, Tim and Sam saw a man taking a photo of a pretty flower. They asked the man if they could be in the photo too. The man said yes and took a photo of Tim and Sam by the flower. They smiled big and said "cheese!" Tim and Sam had a fun day at the park and couldn't wait to play together again.
