Later, Billy saw a small kitten crying under a bush. "Why are you crying?" asked Billy. The kitten looked up and said, "I am lost and can't find my way home." Billy wanted to help, so he said, "Don't cry, little kitten. I will help you find your home." Billy, Ben, and the kitten went on an adventure to find the kitten's home. They walked and talked, and soon they found the kitten's family.

