As they picked the pears, they talked and laughed. Tim said, "These pears look so yummy!" Sue replied, "Yes, they do! Let's share them with everyone!" So, they passed the pears to each other and ate them together. The pears were sweet and juicy, and the children enjoyed them very much.

After they finished eating the pears, they continued to play and pass the ball. They had a great time under the quiet, blue sky. Tim and his friends loved their fun day with the pears and the ball.

