One day, a little girl named Sue went for a walk in the park. She saw a cherry tree full of red cherries. Sue wanted to pick some cherries to eat, but she was too small to reach them. She tried to jump, but she could not get any cherries.

Sue saw a big boy named Tom. She asked, "Can you help me get cherries, please?" Tom said, "Okay, I will help you." Tom tried to reach the cherries, but he could not get them either. Tom had an idea. He said, "I will climb the tree and get the cherries for you."

Tom started to climb the tree. Sue was happy and waited for the cherries. But Tom was not careful. He stumbled and fell from the tree. Tom was sad and hurt. He cried, and Sue felt sad too. They could not get any cherries, and they went home with a bad ending to their day.
<|end|>


