Once upon a time, there was a pretty princess who loved to eat. One day, she was eating her favorite dish of spaghetti and meatballs when she accidentally spilled it all over her pretty dress. She felt embarrassed because everyone was looking at her.

The princess tried to clean the stain off her dress with a napkin, but it didn't work. She thought everyone would laugh at her and make fun of her. But her kind mother told her that it was okay and accidents happen to everyone.

The princess felt better and finished her meal. She learned that it's okay to make mistakes and that her family will always love her no matter what. From that day on, she made sure to be more careful when eating her favorite dish.
