Once upon a time, there was a little duck named Ducky. Ducky loved to play in the water and splash around. One day, Ducky's mommy took him to the mall to buy some new toys. Ducky was so excited to go to the mall, but he was also a little bit fearful because it was his first time going there.

When they arrived at the mall, Ducky saw lots of people and lots of stores. He saw a toy store and asked his mommy if they could go inside. His mommy said yes, and they went inside. Ducky saw lots of toys, but he really wanted a rubber duck. His mommy bought him the rubber duck, and they went back home.

When they got home, Ducky was so happy to play with his new rubber duck. He went to his pond and played with it, splashing around in the water. He was no longer fearful of the mall because he had his new toy to play with. From that day on, Ducky loved going to the mall and always asked his mommy to take him there to buy new toys.
