Once upon a time, there was a little bunny named Benny. Benny loved to bounce around and play all day long. One day, Benny saw a window that was hidden behind a bush. Benny was curious, so he hopped over to the window to take a peek inside.

But when Benny looked through the window, he saw something scary. There was a big, mean dog hiding inside! Benny tried to bounce away, but the dog saw him and started to chase him. Benny hopped as fast as he could, but the dog was too fast.

In the end, the dog caught Benny and he was never seen again. The other bunnies in the meadow missed Benny and wished he had never gone to look through the hidden window.
