Once upon a time, there was a little girl who had a cat. The cat was very comfortable to cuddle with. The little girl loved to spend time with her cat every day. They would play together and have fun.

One day, the little girl went to play outside and left her cat alone at home. While she was gone, a big dog came into their house and scared the cat. The cat ran away and couldn't be found.

The little girl was very sad that she lost her cat. She looked everywhere for her, but she couldn't find her. She realized that she should have stayed home with her cat instead of going outside to play. She learned that spending time with the ones we love is very important because we never know when they might be gone forever.
