Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Lily. She loved to ride her bike in the park with her friends. One day, they saw a big hole in the ground. "What's that?" asked Lily. "It's an underground tunnel," said her friend, Tim. "Let's go explore!"

They rode their bikes down the tunnel and it was very dark. But soon, they saw a light at the end. When they got there, they found a delicious cake waiting for them! "Yum, this cake is so delicious!" said Lily. "Who put it here?" Just then, they heard a voice. "I did," said a friendly old man. "I knew you kids would find it. I put it here for you to enjoy."

Lily and her friends thanked the old man and rode back home, feeling happy and full. From that day on, they always remembered the delicious cake they found underground.
