As they walked, the little bear saw a big tree. He thought it would be fun to climb it, but he was scared. The smart rabbit encouraged him and said, "You can do it! You belong up there!" The little bear felt brave and climbed the tree. From up high, he could see his cozy cave on the hill. He was happy to belong there with his family.
