They searched high and low until Bouncy finally found the nut. Nutty was so happy that he started to applaud. 

"Thank you, Bouncy! You're the best friend ever," Nutty said. 

From that day on, Nutty and Bouncy were the best of friends and they always helped each other when they needed it.
