Once upon a time, there was a girl named Sue. Sue liked to study about the world. One day, she read about a big thing called an earthquake. It made the ground shake a lot. Sue was scared and wanted to learn more.

Sue lived in a clean, small house with her mom and dad. They took care of their home and made sure it was always nice. Sue told her mom and dad about the earthquake. They said not to worry, but Sue still wanted to know how to stay safe.

One day, a real earthquake came to Sue's town. The ground shook a lot and the clean house fell down. Sue, her mom, and her dad were sad. They lost their home and didn't know what to do. The earthquake was very bad, and they had to find a new place to live.
<|end|>


