Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Sue. Sue was nervous because she had to choose a wrap for her mom's birthday gift. She wanted to make her mom happy with the perfect wrap.

Sue went to the store with her dad to look for wraps. There were many colors and patterns to choose from. She saw a red wrap, a blue wrap, and a yellow wrap. Sue thought very hard about which one her mom would like best.

Finally, Sue chose the yellow wrap because it was her mom's favorite color. She felt happy and not nervous anymore. They went home, and Sue wrapped the gift with her dad's help. When her mom opened the gift, she was so happy and loved the yellow wrap. Sue knew she made the right choice.
<|end|>


