One day, a cat named Tom went outside to play. The sun was shining and the ground was dry. Tom saw a big tree and wanted to climb it. He stretched his legs and jumped up onto the tree. He was so happy to be up high.

As Tom climbed higher, he saw a little bird. The bird was sitting on a nail. Tom wanted to say hello to the bird. He stretched his paw out to touch the bird, but the bird flew away. Tom felt sad that the bird did not want to play with him.

Tom decided to climb back down the tree. He stretched his legs and jumped from branch to branch. When he got to the ground, he saw his friend, a dog named Max. Max was running and playing with a ball. Tom joined Max and they played together all day long.
<|end|>


