Once upon a time, there was a little boy named Tim. Tim had a big sister named Sarah. Sarah was going to have a quiz at school. Tim wanted to take the quiz too, but he was too little. He was jealous of Sarah.

One day, Sarah was studying for her quiz. Tim asked, "Can I take the quiz too?" Sarah smiled and said, "Okay, I will permit you to take a fun quiz at home with me." Tim was very happy.

