Amy said, "I lost my ball." The rabbit wanted to make her happy. He said, "I will find your ball." The rabbit looked and looked until he found the ball. He brought it back to Amy.

Amy was very happy. She said, "Thank you, rabbit!" The rabbit was happy too. They played with the ball together. From that day on, Amy and the rabbit were best friends.
