Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Lily. Lily loved to play with her fragile toy dolls. One day, she saw a big closet in her room. She had never seen it before. Lily was very curious about the closet.

Lily opened the closet and saw many pretty dresses. She also found a soft, warm blanket. Lily thought it would be fun to lie down on the blanket with her toy dolls. She took the blanket out of the closet and put it on the floor.

Lily played with her dolls on the blanket for a long time. She pretended they were having a tea party. After a while, Lily felt very tired. She remembered the warm blanket and decided to lie down on it. She fell asleep and had sweet dreams. When Lily woke up, she saw her mommy standing by the closet. Her mommy smiled and said, "I put the blanket in the closet for you to find. I knew you would love it." Lily hugged her mommy and they played with the dolls together.
