Anna liked to play in the park with her friend Ben. They liked to slide, swing, and run on the grass. One day, they saw a big dog with long hair and a wagging tail. The dog was with a lady who smiled at them.

"Can we pet your dog?" Anna asked the lady.

"Sure, his name is Max and he is very harmless. He likes children and he likes to wave his hair when he is happy," the lady said.

Anna and Ben went closer to Max and touched his soft hair. Max licked their faces and made them giggle. He waved his hair and wagged his tail. Anna and Ben waved back at him and said hello.

They played with Max for a while and then said goodbye to him and the lady. They thanked them for letting them pet the dog and went back to their slide and swing. They had a lot of fun in the park that day.
