Lily was a big girl. She wanted to learn how to use the toilet by herself. She asked her mom to teach her.

"Okay, Lily, I will teach you how to use the toilet," her mom said. "But you have to be humble and listen to me."

Lily nodded. She followed her mom to the bathroom. Her mom showed her how to pull down her pants and sit on the toilet. She told her to wait until she felt the pee or the poop come out. Then she showed her how to wipe herself and flush the toilet. She also told her to wash her hands with soap and water.

Lily tried to do everything her mom taught her. She was happy when she peed on the toilet. She was proud when she pooped on the toilet. She smiled when she wiped herself and flushed the toilet. She giggled when she washed her hands.

"Good job, Lily! You are a big girl now!" her mom said. "You learned how to use the toilet by yourself. You were humble and listened to me. I am so proud of you!"

Lily hugged her mom. She said, "Thank you, mom! You are the best teacher! I love you!"
<|end|>


