Anna and Ben are twins. They like to help their mom in the kitchen. Mom is very wise. She knows how to make yummy meals for the family.

One day, mom is busy with work. She asks Anna and Ben to prepare a meal for dinner. She gives them some bread, cheese, ham, eggs, and salad. She tells them to be careful and not make a mess.

Anna and Ben are excited. They put on their aprons and wash their hands. They cut the bread and cheese with a knife. They put ham and cheese on the bread. They make four sandwiches. They crack the eggs and whisk them with a fork. They pour them into a pan and cook them on the stove. They make scrambled eggs. They wash the salad and put it in a bowl. They add some dressing and toss it with a spoon. They make a salad.

They set the table with plates, forks, knives, and napkins. They put the sandwiches, eggs, and salad on the table. They call mom to come and eat. Mom is very happy and proud. She hugs Anna and Ben and thanks them for their help. She says they are very wise and good cooks. They all enjoy the meal together. They smile and laugh. They are a happy family.
<|end|>


