Once upon a time, there was a big tree with many roots. A small boy named Tom lived near the tree. Tom was a fearful boy. He was scared of the big tree and its roots.

One day, Tom's mom told him, "Tom, you need to replace your old toy with a new one." Tom went to the tree to find a new toy. He saw a pretty ball near the tree's roots. He wanted the ball, but he was scared.

Tom took a deep breath and said, "I can do it!" He went near the tree and picked up the ball. Suddenly, the big tree shook, and the roots moved. Tom was very scared and dropped the ball.

