Once upon a time, there was a little cat named Kitty. Kitty loved to lie down in the sun. It made her feel warm and happy. One day, it was very hot outside. Kitty went to lie down in her favorite sunny spot.

Kitty saw a brush on the ground. She thought it was a toy. Kitty played with the brush. She pushed it with her paw and rolled it around. Kitty had lots of fun with the brush.

Soon, Kitty got tired from playing. She lay down next to the brush in the hot sun. Kitty closed her eyes and took a nap. She had a good day playing with her new toy.
<|end|>


