One day, a helpful dog named Buddy saw a big red wagon. Buddy wanted to play with the wagon. He went to his friend, a little girl named Lily. Lily was tired and let out a big yawn.

"Can I play with your wagon, please?" Buddy asked Lily.

"Okay, you can play with it," Lily said with a smile.

Buddy pulled the wagon all around the yard. He had so much fun. He put his toys in the wagon and took them for a ride. The sun was bright and the sky was blue. Buddy and Lily played with the wagon all day long.

As the sun began to set, Buddy and Lily were very tired. They both yawned and smiled at each other. They knew they had a great day together with the big red wagon. They couldn't wait to play again the next day.
<|end|>


