Once upon a time, in a big jungle, there lived a little monkey named Max. Max loved to play all day long. He had many friends, like birds, bugs, and other monkeys.

One day, Max met a big lion named Leo. Max said, "Hi, I am Max. Do you want to play with me?" Leo said, "I am patient, but I am big and strong. Can we play a game that is fun for both of us?"

Max thought for a moment and said, "Yes! Let's play hide and seek!" So Max and Leo played hide and seek in the jungle. Max was fast and good at hiding. Leo was patient and good at finding Max.

They played all day long and had so much fun. Max and Leo loved their new friendship. From that day on, Max and Leo played together in the jungle every day. They were the best of friends, and everyone in the jungle loved to watch them play.
<|end|>


