One day, a little cat named Tim saw a big truck outside his house. The truck had lots of furniture in it. Tim was very excited. He wanted to try sitting on the new furniture. He thought it would be great fun.

Tim went inside the house and saw a big chair. He tried to jump on it, but it was too high. "I will try again," he said to himself. This time, he jumped higher and finally sat on the chair. "Wow, this is great!" Tim said.

Just then, Tim's friend, a little dog named Max, came into the house. Max saw the big chair and wanted to try sitting on it too. Max said, "Can I try sitting on the chair, Tim?" Tim said, "Yes, Max, you can try." Max tried and tried, but he could not jump high enough. Tim helped Max by giving him a little push. Together, they both sat on the chair and had a great time.
