Once upon a time, there was a big rhinoceros named Remy. Remy loved to paint. He would paint all day long. His favorite thing to paint was the sun. He painted the sun with red, yellow, and orange colors.

One day, Remy met a naughty monkey named Max. Max saw Remy painting and said, "Hey, Remy! Can I paint too?" Remy said, "Yes, Max! We can paint together." Max was very happy and they started painting.

But Max was naughty. Instead of painting the sun, Max painted on Remy's face! Remy was sad and said, "Max, that's not nice!" Max felt bad and said, "I'm sorry, Remy. I will be good now." Then, Max and Remy painted a big, beautiful sun together. They became good friends and painted many more pictures together.
