Once upon a time, there was a fearful duck named Ducky. Ducky lived in a small pond with his friends. They liked to play and swim all day. But Ducky was always scared of new things.

One day, Ducky saw a long, green thing in the water. He didn't know what it was. "What is that?" he asked his friend, Froggy. Froggy said, "That is grass. Do not be scared, Ducky. I will help you cut it."

Ducky and Froggy swam to the grass. Froggy showed Ducky how to cut the grass with his beak. They cut and cut until the pond was clean. Ducky was not fearful anymore. He was happy and thanked Froggy for helping him. From that day on, Ducky and Froggy became best friends, and they played happily in the pond.
<|end|>


