One day, a famous bird named Bob lived in a big tree. Bob was very happy. He liked to sing and play with his friends. But Bob had a big problem. He could not scream like a bird. When he tried to scream, it sounded like a cat.

One day, Bob met a new friend named Tim. Tim was a little bug. Tim wanted to play with Bob. "Let's play war," said Tim. "I will be the good bug and you will be the bad bird. When I say 'go', you scream." Bob was scared, but he wanted to try.

They started to play. Tim said, "Go!" and Bob tried to scream like a bird. At first, it sounded like a cat. But then, something changed. Bob's scream became loud and strong like a real bird. Bob was so happy that he could scream like a bird. He thanked Tim for helping him. From that day on, Bob and Tim played war every day, and Bob became famous for his big, strong scream.
<|end|>


