Once upon a time, there was a little boy named Tim. Tim was playing in his room one day when he saw a cable on the floor. He wanted to know what the cable was for. So, he picked it up and took it to his mom.

His mom was in the kitchen making a sandwich. Tim showed her the cable and asked her what it was for. His mom looked at the cable and said, "This is a cable we use to watch TV. But be careful, it can be harsh if you pull on it too hard."

Tim was excited to learn about the cable. He took it back to his room and pretended it was a snake. He played with the cable all day, making sure not to pull on it too hard. And every night, he watched his favorite cartoons on TV with his mom using the cable.
