Once upon a time, there was a boy named Tim. Tim was going on a trip with his family. He had to pack his bag with his toys and clothes. He was very excited.

One day, while packing, Tim saw something strange. It was a sight he had never seen before. A small, green creature was hiding in his room. Tim thought it looked a little stupid, but he was not scared.

Tim and the creature became friends. They played and laughed together. In the end, the creature helped Tim pack his bag. They had a lot of fun on the trip. And they lived happily ever after.
<|end|>


