One day, a pretty bird named Bella was flying in the sky. She saw a big tree with a nest on it. Bella wanted to live in the nest. She flew down and saw that the nest was empty. "This is a nice nest," Bella said.

But then, another bird named Tim came to the tree. Tim saw Bella in the nest and he was not happy. "This is my nest," Tim said. "You cannot stay here." Bella did not want to leave the nest. She wanted to live there too. "Can we share the nest?" Bella asked.

Tim thought about it for a moment. He did not want to share his nest, but he did not want to be a threat to Bella. "Okay, we can share the nest," Tim said. Bella was happy, and they both lived in the nest together. They became good friends and shared the pretty nest on the big tree.
<|end|>


