Once upon a time, there was a boy with an incredible toy. The toy could shoot little balls. The boy's name was Tim.

One day, Tim went to the park with his toy. He played with it all day, shooting the little balls at the trees. He saw his friend, Sue, and wanted to show her his toy. He told Sue, "This toy is so fun, just wait and see!"

Tim set up a row of cans on the ground. He told Sue, "Watch this!" Tim shot the little balls at the cans, and they all fell over. Sue clapped and said, "Wow, Tim! That was incredible!"

From that day on, Tim and Sue played with the incredible toy together, and they had lots of fun. They knew that they had a special toy that brought them closer as friends.
