Once upon a time, there was a big, hairy bear. He lived in a small house in the woods. The bear loved to cook. Every day, he would cook yummy food for his friends.

One day, the bear found a pretty sweater on the ground. It was lost by a little girl who lived nearby. The bear wanted to give the sweater back to her. So, he put on his chef hat and started to cook a big meal for her and her family.

The bear cooked and cooked. He made soup, bread, and a big cake. Then, he put the sweater in a bag and walked to the little girl's house. The little girl and her family were so happy to see the bear and the food he cooked. They thanked the bear and gave him a big hug. The little girl put on her sweater and they all ate the yummy food together. From that day on, they were the best of friends.
