One day, a little girl named Lucy went to the park with her mom. Lucy was very excited to play on the swings and slide. She saw her friends and they all played together. They ran, jumped, and laughed in the warm sun.

After a while, Lucy got tired from playing so much. Her mom saw that she was tired and gave her a big, sweet lollipop. Lucy loved lollipops, and her face lit up with a big smile. She sat on the grass and enjoyed her yummy treat.

Soon, Lucy felt better and was excited to play again. She shared her lollipop with her friends and they all played until the sun went down. They were all tired but happy. Lucy and her mom went home, and she fell asleep with a smile on her face, dreaming of the fun day at the park.
<|end|>


