Once upon a time, there was a curious little dog named Spot. Spot loved to explore and play with his friends in the park. One day, he found a shiny thing on the ground. It was a license!

Spot wanted to add the license to his collection of treasures. He picked it up with his mouth and ran home. Spot showed his treasures to his friend, Kitty. Kitty was very curious too.

Together, Spot and Kitty added the license to their collection. They were very happy and proud. From that day on, they continued to explore and find more treasures to add to their collection. And they lived happily ever after.
