Once upon a time, there was a small lizard. The lizard lived in a big tree. Every day, the lizard would watch the sun rise. The lizard had a friend, a bird. The bird could fly high in the sky. The lizard was envious of the bird.

One day, the lizard said to the bird, "I wish I could rise like you and touch the sky." The bird said, "You can try to climb the tree and reach the top. Maybe you will feel like you are in the sky."

The lizard tried to climb the tree. It was hard, but the lizard did not give up. The bird helped the lizard by cheering him on. At last, the lizard reached the top of the tree. The lizard felt happy and proud. The lizard and the bird watched the sun rise together.
