Once upon a time, there was a charming little frog. He lived near a small pond. He liked to jump and play all day long. He had many friends who lived there too. They all had fun together.

One day, the frog saw a big mess near the pond. It was very dirty. The frog wanted to help, so he started to wipe the mess with his small hands. He worked very hard. His friends saw him and they all came to help.

But the mess was too big for them. They wiped and wiped, but it did not go away. The pond became dirty too. The charming little frog and his friends could not play there anymore. They were very sad. The bad mess had changed their fun pond forever.
