Once upon a time, in a cheerful garden, there lived a little plant. The plant was very happy because it had many friends. They played together all day long.

One day, a big mean bug came to the garden. The bug wanted to eat the little plant and its friends. The plant knew it had to fight to save everyone. The plant was scared, but it had to be brave.

The next day, the plant and its friends made a plan. They all fought the big mean bug together. And guess what? They won! The bug went away, and the little plant and its friends were safe again. They were all very happy and played together in their cheerful garden forever.
