Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Amy. She lived in a small house with her mom and dad. They had a big, red oven in the kitchen. Amy loved to help her mom bake cookies in the oven.

One day, Amy's mom said, "Amy, let's bake cookies today!" Amy was so happy. She put on her comfortable apron and went to the kitchen. Her mom pointed at the oven and said, "We will use this oven to bake our cookies."

Amy and her mom mixed the dough and put it on a tray. They opened the oven door and carefully put the cookies inside. Amy pointed at the cookies and said, "Mom, I can't wait to eat them!"

After a while, the cookies were ready. Amy and her mom took them out of the oven and let them cool. They sat on comfortable chairs and enjoyed the warm, yummy cookies together. It was a perfect day for Amy and her mom.
