Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Lily. She loved to play outside in the warm sunshine with her friends. One day, as she was playing in the garden, she saw a beautiful flower starting to bloom. She ran to her mommy and said, "Mommy, look at the pretty flower! It's blooming!"

