Lily was so upset and started to cry. Her mommy came over and asked what was wrong. Lily replied, "I broke the pretty flower and the gem inside it. I'm sorry mommy." Her mommy hugged her and said, "It's okay, accidents happen. But we must learn from our mistakes and not take things that don't belong to us."
