Once upon a time, there was a fish named Fin. Fin lived in a big, blue ocean with his fish friends. One day, Fin saw a long hook in the water. He knew it was dangerous, so he swam away fast. But one of his friends got stuck on the hook! Fin wanted to help his friend escape. He swam over to the hook and bit it with his sharp teeth. The hook came loose and his friend was free! Fin felt happy that he could help his friend. From then on, Fin and his friends were more careful of the long hooks in the water.
<|end|>


