Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Lily. She went to the park with her mommy and daddy. At the park, there was a big gate that opened and closed. Lily liked to watch the gate go up and down. She said, "I can do that too!" and tried to push the gate. But it was too heavy for her.

After playing on the swings and slide, Lily felt uncomfortable. She had sand in her shoes and her clothes were dirty. So, her mommy and daddy helped her clean up and put on fresh clothes. Then, they went home and had a yummy snack. Lily was happy and tired from all the fun she had at the park.
<|end|>


