Once upon a time, there was a little mouse named Max. Max had a long tail that he loved to wag when he was happy. One day, Max went on an adventure to find some cheese. He walked and walked until he came across a big wall. Max tried to climb the wall, but it was too difficult for him. 

Just then, a friendly bird named Bella flew by. "Hi Max! What are you doing?" asked Bella. "I'm trying to reach the cheese on the other side of this wall, but it's too difficult for me," replied Max. "I can help you!" said Bella. 

Bella flew over the wall and brought back some cheese for Max. Max was so happy and grateful. "Thank you, Bella! You have a very kind heart," said Max, wagging his tail happily. From that day on, Max and Bella became good friends and went on many more adventures together.
<|end|>


