Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Lily. She loved to play outside with her friends. One day, while playing hide-and-seek, Lily found a delicate butterfly with colorful wings. She wanted to catch it, but didn't want to hurt it. 

Lily asked her friend, "Can you help me catch the butterfly?" 

Her friend replied, "Sure! Let's use this well to catch it." 

Lily and her friend carefully used the well to catch the butterfly and then gently placed it on a seat made of leaves. They watched the butterfly for a while before letting it fly away. 

From that day on, Lily and her friend made sure to always be delicate with nature and the creatures around them.
<|end|>


