Once upon a time, there was a white squash. It was the biggest squash that anyone had ever seen. Everybody wanted to cut it but no one knew how.

One day, a brave little boy came along and said he could cut it. Everyone laughed, but the little boy said he'd give it a try.

He picked up a tiny knife and got to work. Everyone was surprised when he actually managed to cut it.

The little boy pulled off the top, and inside he found the biggest, juiciest squash he had ever seen! Everyone was so happy and shared it together. The little boy was the happiest of all!
