Once upon a time, there was a small boy named Jamie. Jamie loved to play outside and explore the world around him. One day, Jamie decided to go on an adventure. 

He walked towards a big blue door, which was open. He stepped on the door and it made a loud sound. He was so amazed and jumped around the door. Then, suddenly the door closed!

Jamie was scared and started to cry. He didn't know what to do. He looked around, but there was no way to open the door. But then, he remembered something his mom told him, he needed to find something that was blue to open the door. 

Jamie looked around and saw a small blue flower. He grabbed the flower, put it inside the door and it opened. He was so happy and excited. The adventure could end and Jamie was safe.
<|end|>


