Once upon a time, there was a chubby bear named Fred. Fred liked to relax and sleep, especially on sunny days. He would find the softest trees and take a wide nap. One day, Fred was having a special nap. He heard two people talking nearby. 

"Fred looks so healthy," said one of the people.
"Yes, he's chubby and looks very relaxed," said the other.

Fred couldn't believe what he heard. He thought to himself, "Am I really that chubby?"

Fred opened one eye, slightly adjusting his position so he could get a better view of himself. He could see his reflection in a nearby puddle. He realised he was definitely chubby, but he also thought it looked kinda cute. He felt happy and relaxed again. 

Fred slowly got up and walked away, feeling wide and content.
<|end|>


