Once upon a time there was a furry bunny named Billy. He lived in a big park with lots of shade and that's where he loved to hang out. 
One day, Billy saw a beautiful bunny named Harriet. She was very kind and came over to say hi. Billy thought she was the prettiest bunny he had ever seen. 
Billy asked Harriet to marry him, and she was very happy. But then, a problem occurred. Billy's family didn't like the shade Harriet was from - they didn't think she was the right bunny for Billy. 
Billy and Harriet were very sad. They didn't know what to do.
But then, Billy's family saw how much Billy and Harriet loved each other, and in the end they agreed to let them marry. 
Billy and Harriet were so happy that they married under the shade of the trees in the park, and they celebrated long into the night.
<|end|>


