Once there was a little boy who was playing with his toy car on the floor. He rolled it really fast across the couch but he didn't see the sharp nail sticking out. The nail scratched the car. The little boy was very sad. He tried to push the nail in but it was too sharp. Just then he heard his mom's voice. She said, "Come inside now, it's getting late." The little boy sadly put the car away and went inside. His mom never noticed the nail and his car stayed scratched.
<|end|>


