Once upon a time there was a little boy called Jack. He was so excited because it was his birthday! Jack had lots of presents under his tree. He wanted to open the presents but he had to wait until everyone was here.

Finally, everyone arrived and it was time to open his presents. Everyone was gathered around Jack and he started to open each one.

Jack looked closely at the first present and he saw something special inside. He examined it carefully and then shouted, "Ooh, it's a ball!"
Jack kept opening one after another and suddenly he found an open box. Inside it he found a special toy car, it was so fine! 

Everyone was so excited for Jack and his dad said, "Oh my! What a wonderful present! Let's take it outside and play with it". 

Jack and his dad went outside and Jack jumped in his toy car and started to move around. It was so much fun and Jack was so happy!
<|end|>


