Once upon a time there was a girl who wanted a watch. The watch was very attractive and she really wanted it.

One day she asked her mom if she could have the watch and her mom said yes. The girl was so excited and she ran to get the watch.

When she finally had the watch she went outside to celebrate. She held the watch up high and spun around with it over her head.

But something bad happened. The watch slipped out of her hand and fell to the ground. She looked down and saw that the watch was broken.

The girl was so sad and she no longer felt like celebrating. She put the broken watch back in its box and said goodbye.
<|end|>


