There was a jolly family that had been waiting for a very long time. They had all been so excited for something special to arrive.

Finally, one day, something arrived. It was an x-ray. The family was amazed and they looked at the x-ray together. It showed a very special thing inside their family.

The family smiled when they looked at it. It was a happy picture that made them very happy and jolly.

The next day the family made a plan. They were going to have a party to celebrate the special thing that had arrived. All the family's friends and family were invited, and they had a great time. Everyone was very jolly.

The family was so happy that the special thing had arrived. They all thanked the x-ray for bringing them such good news.
<|end|>


