Once there was an egg. It was alone and it felt sad. Suddenly, it heard a funny sound. It was a sound like 'snap'.

The egg looked around and saw a funny rabbit. The rabbit was snapping its fingers. The egg was really excited. It wanted to snap its fingers too.

The rabbit showed the egg how to snap its fingers. The egg was so excited! It snapped and snapped and snapped. It was so fun!

The egg and the rabbit were having the best time. They snapped their fingers until the sun went down. Then, they said goodbye and the egg went home.
<|end|>


