Once upon a time, there was a wet flame. It spread everywhere and made lots of noise. Everyone was very scared. But then, a brave boy came to help. He touched the wet flame and the flame went away. Everyone was so happy! The boy said that the wet flame wouldn't come back. Everyone cheered and thanked the boy, who smiled and said goodbye. Everyone said he was a brave, special boy - and they were right!
