Once upon a time there was a nice bug. His name was Bob and he lived in the garden. Every day he would perform fun tricks in the garden to impress his friends. 

One day, Bob was doing his tricks when he saw a rude insect. The insect was very noisy and kept bothering Bob. Bob was not happy and tried to tell the rude insect to stop being so loud. 

The rude insect refused to listen and kept making more noise. Bob had had enough and decided to perform an extra special trick. In an instant, Bob wiggled his antennae and flew away.

The rude insect was shocked and watched as Bob flew off. Bob waved goodbye to his friends and flew away with a smile on his face.

And he lived happily ever after. The End.
<|end|>


