Once upon a time, there was a brave girl named Penelope. She was always looking up to the sky and dreaming of what she could do. One day, she said, "I want to go to the top of the sky!" 

Penelope was a bit scared, but she was determined to try. She looked for a way to the top. She ran, she jumped, she tried to climb and she got more and more tired. But she didn't stop!

Finally, she reached the top of the sky. It was tough, but she was very happy. Penelope looked down from the sky and cried out in joy. She said, "I did it! I made it to the top of the sky!"
<|end|>


