<|asst|>
Once upon a time there was a wise bear who wanted to have a fire. He asked his friends what he should do and they recommended he go to the woods to get some wood. So the wise bear headed off to the woods, and after some searching he found what he needed. He gathered some sticks, twigs and a big log, and went back to his cave. He worked very hard and was able to get the fire going! He was very proud of himself for making such a wise decision. The fire kept him warm and he was very happy.
<|end|>


