Once upon a time there was a man who loved pigs. He had an ancient pig that he kept in the barn. Every day he would feed the pig and bring it some fresh water.

One day, the man needed to go to town and he thought that he would bring the pig with him. So he got the ancient pig and put it in a cart. He then set off for town.

When they reached town, people were amazed to see the man with the ancient pig. They had never seen anything like it before! Everyone wanted to pet the pig, but the man wouldn't let them because it was so special.

The man and the ancient pig made it back home safely and the pig returned to its home in the barn. Every day since then, the man still brings the ancient pig food and water.
