At first Amelia was scared and did not want to do it. It looked too hard. But Amelia was brave and decided to give it a try. Amelia's mum showed her how to stir the spaghetti.

Then they added some sauce and spices. Amelia was so proud when it smelled delicious. She stirred the spaghetti more and it started to look like you could eat it.

Finally, it was time to eat. Amelia was so happy that she had cooked the spaghetti all by herself. She thought she was the best cook ever! From then on, Amelia and her mum cooked spaghetti together every week.
