One day, Amy was playing at the park with her friends. Suddenly, she noticed a man standing nearby. He was a stranger. Amy was scared of him at first, because he seemed very strange. 

"Who are you?" she asked, feeling a bit shy.

The stranger smiled at Amy and said "My name is Jim, and I am here to meet you". 

Amy was still scared, but she knew that it was okay to meet strangers. She slowly walked towards Jim and shook his hand. 

"It's nice to meet you, Jim," said Amy, warming up to him. 

Jim reached out and gave her a hug and said "It's nice to meet you too, Amy!" 

Amy smiled, no longer feeling so shy. She had found a new friend!
