Once upon a time, there lived a little girl. She had a warm hat that she loved to wear, even when it was chilly outside. One day she decided to go for a walk outside in the icy air. 

She wandered around for a little while, checking out the winter scenery. Suddenly, she slipped and fell on the ground. Her hat flew out of her hands and rolled away. She tried to catch up to it, but it had already spread far away.

The little girl was so sad that she had lost her favourite hat. She searched the area and asked people if they had seen it, but she couldn't find it anywhere. She was so cold and upset that she decided to head home. 

When she got there, she was so surprised to see her hat lying on the floor! Even though her journey had been filled with sadness, in the end it had a happy ending. She put on the hat, smiled, and snuggled up in a warm blanket.
