Once upon a time there lived a little girl named Jane. She lived in a big beautiful house with a normal lawn. One day a very strange thing happened in Jane's backyard. While she was playing in the grass she noticed something very strange - a big, bright blue elephant!

Jane gasped in surprise and ran to her mother to tell her. She asked, "Mama, what is that big blue elephant doing in our lawn?" 

Her mother smiled and said, "Well Jane, it's a bit of a surprise. That blue elephant is here to take you on a special adventure today." 

Jane was so excited she felt like she was going to soar off into the sky! When the adventure was over, the blue elephant gently walked back over to the lawn. Jane waved goodbye as the elephant disappeared.

From that day on, Jane always expected something unusual to happen when she went out to play on the normal lawn.
