One day, a little girl was walking in to the woods. She was wearing a thick jacket. Suddenly, she heard a loud noise. The little girl started to shiver and she couldn't stop! She was so scared.

Then, she saw a big black dog wearing a collar. The big dog was looking at her. But, it didn't bark at her. Instead, it started to wag its tail. The little girl was still scared, but she slowly felt better.

The dog was friendly and it started to follow her. The little girl was feeling a bit warmer now because the dog had a thick fur coat.

They walked until they were out of the woods. The little girl thanked the dog before they went their separate ways. From that day on, the little girl was no longer scared to go into the woods.
