Once there was a little girl named Lucy. She used to wander around the woods near her house every day. One day she came across a big hole in the ground. She had never seen a hole that big before so she was curious and she decided to have a look. 

As she was wandering around the hole, she got a little too close and she fell right in! She was stuck inside the hole and it was very dark and miserable. Lucy was scared and she started to cry. 

Then, all of a sudden, a big dog came running towards the hole. His name was Barky. He could see Lucy was stuck and he started to bark. Soon enough, someone heard him and came to help Lucy. 

When the people arrived, they managed to get Lucy out of the hole. She was so relieved and she gave Barky a big hug to say thank you. Lucy was very happy and she never went near that hole again.
