John went to the station with his dad. He saw a big train and lots of people walking around. He was very excited. Dad showed him how to use the ticket machine. It was smooth to touch and John could press the buttons. 

John used the ticket to get on the train. It was very big and it felt smooth when it started to move. His dad was with him and told him to look through the window. He saw lots of trees and houses go past. John was so happy. 

