Once there was a little girl called Jen. She had a Garage which was very distant from her house. One day Jen heard a strange noise coming from the garage. She went to investigate. When Jen got to the garage she saw a big, blue bird. The bird looked at Jen and said "Hello! What is your name?" Jen was very surprised but she answered "My name is Jen!" "But what are you doing here" Jen asked. The bird replied, "I am looking for a place to rest, can I stay in the garage?" Jen smiled and answered, "Yes, you can stay in the garage." From that day, the bluebird and Jen became friends. They played all sorts of games together and even shared secrets. Jen was so happy to have a new friend.
