The second child said, "I'm scared." 
But the first child said, "It's okay! I will help you."

The two children began to climb the enormous rock. When they reached the top, the little one pointed left and said, "Look! There's something shiny over there!"

The two children carefully climbed down the rock and slowly approached the shiny thing in the distance. When they finally reached it, the little one grinned and said, "It's a surprise for me!"

