The two children raced around the field, finding more and more amazing rocks. Soon, they had an enormous pile of colorful rocks at their feet. The little one said, "This is the best rock hunt ever!"

The two children spent the rest of the day playing with the colorful rocks, forgetting all about their fears of the enormous rock. Through their rock hunt, they had learned that life can be filled with wonderful
