Once upon a time there was a boy who was playing in his modern bedroom. He liked to run around and poke his pillow. One day, the boy got a bit too excited and started to poke the pillow very hard. But he didn't realize that the pillow had a hidden, old button at the back. Suddenly, the button began to beep and the whole room started shaking! The boy was so scared that he started crying.

Suddenly, a big, old man appeared in the room and scowled at the boy. the boy was trembling and the old man asked him why he had been poking the pillow so hard. The boy apologized and said that he just wanted to have some fun. 

The old man smiled and then he said, "as punishment, I have to take your modern bedroom away from you! Goodbye!" The boy started to sob and he tried to plead but the old man had already gone. 

The boy was sad and upset. He never got to play and poke his pillow in his modern bedroom ever again.
<|end|>


