Once upon a time, there lived a little boy called Jack. He loved exploring outside in the garden. One day, Jack found a nut on the ground and thought it looked delicious.

Jack shouted out to his dad, "Dad! Look what I found!" His dad came over and said, "That looks filthy! I wouldn't recommend you eat it!"

Jack was a little bit sad, but he still wanted to try it. He asked his dad, "Can I please have a try?" His dad thought for a moment and then said, "Okay, but just a try."

Jack carefully picked up the nut and took a bite. He immediately spat it out and said, "It's yucky!" His dad laughed and said, "See, I told you. I wouldn't recommend it!"

The End.
<|end|>


