Once upon a time, there was a boy named Sammy who didn't like his job. Each day he was asked to work with a dull staff, and every time he had to do it, he would sneeze. Sammy started to want an easier job, so he thought of a plan.

On Monday he sneezed very strongly, and his boss was annoyed. He told Sammy that he would have to do more work if he kept sneezing like that. Sammy was worried and kept working with the dull staff.

The next day he decided to try something different. He worked hard and helped his boss in any way he could. His boss was very pleased, and even gave him a special lunch as a reward.

Sammy learnt a very important lesson; that hard work and a positive attitude can help you achieve more than anything else. He realized that the dull staff was not so bad after all. From then on, his hard work and enthusiasm were rewarded, and Sammy was very happy.
<|end|>


