Once there was a smart little girl named Mary. Mary liked to play on the shore. One day, she went to the shore with her mommy and they played together. They built sand castles and looked for pretty seashells. Mary picked the prettiest ones, and she showed them to her mommy.

After they were done playing, Mary and her mommy had a picnic. They ate crackers and cheese, and drank juice. It was a lot of fun. 

Mary and her mommy stayed at the shore till the sun went down. Then they went back home, and Mary felt very happy. She could not wait to play on the shore again soon.
