Once upon a time there was a lady who wanted to buy a ladder. She went to the shop and saw many ladders in the store window. She saw one that was really attractive and she decided to buy it.

The lady went into the shop and said to the clerk, "I want to buy the ladder in the window, please." The clerk smiled and said, "Yes." He took the ladder off the shelf and started to carry it out.

Suddenly, the lady started to sneeze. She sneezed so loudly that the clerk put the ladder down and said, "Are you ok?" The lady said, "Yes, I'm just sneezing." After she finished sneezing, she bought the ladder and went on her way.

The end.
