The sky was cloudy and it started to rain. It was warm and the rain was mixed with sunshine.

The children played outside, running around a big track. They were having lots of fun, jumping and laughing. But soon their clothes and shoes got dirty from all the running.

The track was muddy and slippery from the rain and the children had to be careful not to slip. Even though it was raining, the children didnâ€™t want to go inside. They kept playing and running around in the rain until they were all exhausted.

