One day, two friends, Bob and Tim, were walking near the beach. They spotted a tube in the sand. They thought it might be something fun to play with so they ran up to it. The tube was smelly. Bob and Tim still decided to play with it.

They started running around, having fun. Soon, the tube started to rise. They got scared and started running away. But the tube kept getting bigger and bigger. It was too heavy for Bob and Tim to move.

They screamed for help, but nobody came. As the tube rose higher and higher, the air got thinner and thinner. They started getting dizzy and they couldn't breathe. The tube quickly reached the sky and their bodies became too weak to keep running.

Suddenly, the tube disappeared into the sky, taking Bob and Tim with it. They were never seen again.
<|end|>


