Once there were two twins, Jack and Jill. They were different in every way. Jack was grumpy and Jill was happy. Every day they would play in their nice garden.

Once, Jack wanted to add something to their garden. He was grumpy about it and Jill was excited. She thought it would make the garden even better.

So Jack and Jill went out to find what Jack wanted. They looked and looked until finally they found the perfect thing. They added it to the garden and it looked great!

Jack and Jill were both so happy. The garden was now even better and it made Jack less grumpy. From then on, Jack was always happy to add something new to the garden.
