The girl smiled and said, "Yes, I want to go to the gym with you. I want to be fit too!" 

The man smiled and said, "Then it's settled. I will invite you to the gym every day." 

The girl quickly said, "Yay!" 

Every day they went to the gym. They worked out, ran and did exercises. The girl felt better each day and saw her body getting stronger and fitter. 

The man was glad to have invited the girl to the gym and they both worked hard and had fun. 

The girl was so proud of herself for getting fit. It was all thanks to her friend who invited her to the gym.
