Once there was a little boy named Jack who was very intelligent. His mom was always worried about him. One day, his mom send him to the park to play. He was so excited to go. 

When he got to the park, it was very windy. Jack noticed the leaves blowing quickly in the wind and he decided to chase after them. Soon enough, the wind got too strong and Jack started to blow away with it! His mom saw this, and she became very worried.

She started to run after him, but she couldn't catch him. No matter how hard she tried, the wind was too powerful. Jack kept getting further and further away and soon enough, he was out of sight. His mom was very sad.

Jack never came back and his mom was filled with worry. She never stopped thinking about him and she never gave up hope. But, no matter how intelligent and brave Jack was, the wind had the power to send him away forever.
