Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Sally. She was only three years old and very curious. One day she was playing in the kitchen when she heard a whisper coming from the sink. She couldn't believe her ears! She crept closer and the whispering got louder. She waited and listened carefully. Suddenly, she heard a loud voice coming from the sink. It said, "Hello Sally". Sally was so scared she jumped back. Then the voice said, "Don't worry, I just want to be your friend". Sally was still scared but she shook her head yes. The voice asked her if she wanted to go on an adventure. She said yes and took a deep breath. Then the voice said, "Jump in the sink and I'll take you to a magical place". Sally hesitated but the voice kept talking. "Come on Sally, it's going to be fun"! So Sally jumped into the sink and, with a loud splash, she was gone. 

Sally had the most amazing adventure. She flew through the sky with the voice and saw so many amazing things. Eventually, she was back in the kitchen with the voice still whispering in her ear. It said, "Remember this day and don't be scared. I'll be here for you if you ever need me". Sally nodded and the voice whispered goodbye. She watched as the sink filled with water and the voice went away. She smiled and whispered back, "Thank you".
