Once upon a time there was a little girl named Claire. Claire liked to go on adventures. One day she decided to search for some paint. She grabbed her bag and began running around her garden. She looked everywhere but she couldn't find any paint. Suddenly she saw a slow movement out of the corner of her eye. A butterfly! Claire followed the butterfly until it stopped near a big tree.There it was - a jar of paint! Claire was so happy that she searched and found the paint. She carefully opened the jar and saw all of the bright colors. She wanted to paint the tree so she grabbed her brush and began to make beautiful pictures. Her tree was now full of color and it looked so pretty! Claire was so happy with her slow search and her beautiful paintings.
<|end|>


