Once upon a time there was a boy who was very adventurous. He wanted to explore space.

One day he asked his mom, "Mom, can I go to space?"

His mom replied, "No, my dear, space is too far away."

But his mom showed him a picture of space. It was filled with stars and planets, and the boy was amazed.

He asked, "Can I go there? Can I explore space?"

His mom said, "Maybe someday you can. But right now you must stay here. But I know you can be adventurous and explore even here."

So the boy explored the park nearby and imagined he was in space. He pretended he was flying among the stars and planets and had an exciting adventure. He had so much fun!
<|end|>


