Once upon a time, there was a pink bunny. The bunny loved to jump. Every day he would jump all around his green yard.

One day, while he was jumping, he heard a noise. He stopped jumping and looked all around. He couldn't see where the noise was coming from. He jumped closer to the noise and saw that the noise was coming from a big pink flower!

The bunny was very excited. He jumped around the flower and the noise got louder and louder. He was sure that this flower would be his friend.

So, every day the bunny would jump and the flower would make noise. They were the best of friends. The bunny was so happy!
