Mike and Max were so excited and partied their way over to the little puppy. The puppy was so cute and clever, but seemed very scared. They tried to pet it but it ran away. 

Mike had an idea. He took a piece of cheese from his pocket and held it up for the puppy to see. The puppy came close to Mike and sniffed the cheese. 

Mike said, "It's ok puppy, come with us! We'll be your friends". The puppy was happy and partied with Mike and Max. The three of them became best friends and went on many adventures together. The End.
