Once upon a time, there was a rich ant named Bob. Bob loved to stir the earth around his home each day. He carefully dug small rows and would fill them with soil so he could plant something. 

One day, Bob was stirring the earth and something magical happened. As he started to make a new row, he heard a deep thumping sound. He was so amazed! He kept stirring and the thump got louder.

Eventually he uncovered a magical box full of treasure! He was so rich and excited! He opened the chest and the thumping sound got louder and louder. 

It turns out that a beautiful butterfly had been in the box the whole time! She was so happy to be free and fluttered about in joyous freedom. Bob and the butterfly enjoyed the beautiful day together and Bob always cherished the amazing treasure he found.
