Once upon a time, there were two best friends called Laura and Adam. One day, they decided to go and buy some yummy ice cream. Laura wanted to go to the shop, but Adam suggested that they should go to the toilet first. Laura did not understand why, but he insisted so she followed him.

When they got to the toilet, Adam asked Laura to wait outside. She waited and waited, but Adam did not come out for a very long time. After almost an hour, Laura regretfully decided to go inside. She opened the door and saw Adam eating all the ice cream from the shop!

Laura was terribly angry and shouted, "Why did you do this?!" Adam sheepishly replied, "I'm sorry, I couldn't resist. I really regret it now."

Laura was so upset that they could not go and buy any yummy ice cream, so she sadly walked home without Adam. Adam never made the same mistake again. He had learned his lesson; don't do anything you'll regret!
<|end|>


