Once upon a time, there were two friends, Alex and Alison. They wanted to drink something special on a hot day. Alex said, "Let's go and get some juice. I want a spicy juice!"

Alison didn't like the idea. She said, "No, let's get something else. How about a gray juice?"

Alex was not happy about this. He wanted something more special. But Alison just wanted a gray juice.

So, they began to argue. Alex said, "It's too boring! I want something else." But Alison was not ready to change her mind.

Suddenly, they heard a voice. It was their mom. "How about a blend of both! We can mix a spicy juice and a gray juice together. That way, you both can have what you want."

The two friends thought it was a great idea. So, they went to the kitchen and mixed a spicy and a gray juice together. After drinking, they both agreed that this was the best drink they had ever tasted!
<|end|>


