Once there was a regular, little girl named Sally. Sally worried a lot about the world and what would happen in the future. One day, Sally's mom told her a secret. She said, "Sally, do you know about treasures? Treasures are special, magical things that can make your worries go away!" Sally was very excited and asked, "Where can I find a treasure?" Her mom smiled and said, "You don't need to look for it, Sally. Your treasure is inside of you!" Sally smiled and knew that her mom was right. Whenever she was worried or scared, she would close her eyes and find her treasure within her heart.
