Once upon a time there was a smart little girl named Franny. She loved to wear her bracelet everywhere she went. One day, she was walking to the park and saw a seat. She thought it would be nice to sit in the seat, so she did. 

But then Franny realized the seat wasn't just empty. There was someone else there! It was an old lady in a grey dress. The old lady was not happy when Franny sat next to her. She yelled at Franny and grabbed her bracelet! 

Franny was very sad and tried to get her bracelet back, but the old lady wouldn't give it. Franny sadly went home without her bracelet.

Moral of the story: Be careful who you trust!
