Once upon a time there was a little girl called Wendy. She was happy and kind and loved to play in the park.

One day, Wendy decided to take a snack to the park to share with her friends. She was so excited and full of joy! 

When she got to the park, she found all of her friends. She shared her snack and everyone was happy. But then, one of her friends was rude and started shouting and hitting people. Wendy was very sad. 

Wendy decided to hug her friend in order to make them feel better. She hugged her friend tight, and the rude behavior stopped. 

Everyone was happy again, and Wendy and her friends played in the park for the rest of the day.  They all decided that being kind was way more fun than being rude.
