Once upon a time, there was a rat named Sam. He was both small and sneaky. He liked to play hide and seek, and it was his favorite game.

One day, Sam was walking near a deep pond. He wanted to go to the other side of the pond, but there was no bridge. So Sam tried to balance on a log to get across.

He wobbled to one side, and then the other. Sam stayed focused and balanced with his eyes closed. He gently swayed back and forth. Finally, he made it to the other side!

Sam was so happy and proud of himself. He had balanced on the log, and made it safely across the deep pond! From then on, Sam was the king of balance.
<|end|>


