A little boy noticed an unusual watch lying in his garden. He picked it up and noticed it was ticking, so he decided to keep it. 

The boy often took his watch out of his pocket while playing to look at it. One day he noticed something sparkling from inside it. He opened the watch and found a magic stone. 

The boy was so excited! He waved his hand over the stone and noticed that it began to glow. He looked around and noticed a rainbow in the sky. It was so beautiful and unusual. 

