Once upon a time there was a boy who loved movies. He loved them so much that he kept rushing to the cinema every day. Every time he went, he would find a different movie to watch, as he never got tired of watching them.

One day, he rushed to the cinema again, but something strange happened: the movie had already finished. Disappointed, he was about to go home, when he noticed that a new movie had started. He was so excited he rushed into the auditorium.

The movie was so mesmerising that he sat there for the whole day, not wanting to leave. His mom noticed how persistent he was and thought it was really amazing. He ended up watching the same movie twice and loved it.

The boy went to the cinema every day from then on and it became his best friend. He loved his movies and the cinema, which were always there for him!
