Once upon a time, there was a twin brother and sister. The brother was called Jack and the sister was called Jill. They were always playing together and they loved having fun.

One day when they were playing outside, they heard a strange sound coming from the nearby woods. The sound sounded like someone singing. So Jack and Jill decided to investigate.

They crept quietly into the woods and soon enough, they saw what was making the noise. A beautiful bird! But this was not a normal bird, it was unusual - it could actually sing words!

The bird was singing the same phrase over and over again. Jack finally worked out the words the bird was singing: "Something special is coming soon".

Jack and Jill were very excited by this. They couldn't wait to see what was going to happen next! They rushed home, talking about what the bird's singing could mean.

Days went by and nothing happened. But finally, one afternoon, there was a knock at the door and when Jack and Jill opened it, they saw the most amazing thing - the bird was there!

The bird had brought them a gift, it was something special! What a surprise!

Jack, Jill and the bird spent the rest of the day playing together, singing and having lots of fun.

The bird had made the day even more special, with its unusual singing.
<|end|>


