"Hey, can I push the bell?" Timmy asked a man who was sitting on a bench.

"Sure, go ahead," the man replied.

Timmy pushed the bell with all his might, but it wouldn't budge. "It's too heavy," Timmy said.

"That's because it's made of metal. Metal is very strong," the man explained.

Timmy was amazed. He had never seen anything so strong before. From that day on, he made it his mission to become even stronger so he could push the bell one day.
