Once upon a time, there was a cute little bunny named Benny. Benny loved to hop around in the forest and play with his friends. One day, Benny was hopping along when he saw a big swamp. He thought it looked like a great place to explore.

Benny hopped into the swamp and started to look around. Suddenly, he heard a loud noise. "What was that?" Benny asked himself. Then, he heard it again. "Oh no!" Benny said. "I think I'm going to fall!"

Sure enough, Benny fell into the swamp. He was stuck in the mud and couldn't get out. "Help! Help!" Benny cried. But no one could hear him. Just when Benny thought he would be stuck forever, his friends came to the rescue. They pulled him out of the swamp and helped him clean off.

From that day on, Benny learned to be more careful when exploring new places. He was grateful for his friends and promised to always stick together with them.
