But then Lily's mommy reminded her that she had her own special purse that she loved very much. Lily realized her mommy was right and felt happy again. She played with Emma and they had fun together. 

When it was time to go home, Lily hugged her mommy and said, "I love you and my purse too!" Her mommy smiled and hugged her back. They walked home together, happy and content.
