<|asst|>
Anna liked to play with her doll, Lily. Lily had a pink dress, yellow hair and blue eyes. Anna took Lily everywhere with her. She hugged her, talked to her and pretended to feed her.

One day, Anna and Lily went to the park with Mommy. Anna put Lily on the swing and pushed her gently. Lily smiled and said, "Whee!" Anna smiled back and said, "You are my best friend, Lily."

But then, a big boy came and grabbed Lily from the swing. He said, "This is my doll now!" and ran away. Anna was very sad and angry. She cried and shouted, "Give Lily back! She is mine!"

Mommy heard Anna and ran to help her. She saw the big boy and said, "Hey, that is not your doll. That is Anna's doll. Give it back to her right now!" The big boy was scared of Mommy and threw Lily on the ground. He said, "Fine, take your stupid doll!" and ran away.

Anna and Mommy picked up Lily from the ground. They saw that Lily was hurt. Her dress was torn, her hair was messy and her eye was broken. Anna cried and said, "Oh no, Lily! You are broken! I'm sorry, Lily!"

Mommy hugged Anna and said, "Don't worry, Anna. We can fix Lily. We can take her to the repair shop. They can make her look like new again. They can sew her dress, comb her hair and fix her eye. She will be your original Lily again."

Anna wiped her tears and said, "Really, Mommy? Can they do that?" Mommy nodded and said, "Yes, they can. Come on, let's go to the repair shop. I'm sure they will be very nice to Lily."

Anna and Mommy took Lily to the repair shop. They met a nice lady who said, "Hello, what can I do for you?" Mommy said, "We need to repair this doll. She had an accident at the park. Can you make her look like new again?" The nice lady said, "Of course, I can. I love dolls. I will take good care of her. It will take some time, but I will make her as good as original."

Anna and Mommy thanked the nice lady and left Lily with her. They went to have some ice cream and waited for Lily to be ready. After a while, the nice lady called them and said, "Your doll is ready. Come and see her."

Anna and Mommy went back to the repair shop. They saw Lily on the counter. She looked beautiful. Her dress was mended, her hair was shiny and her eye was fixed. She smiled and said, "Hello, Anna. I missed you." Anna was very happy and said, "Lily, you are back! You look amazing! Thank you, nice lady, for fixing Lily. You are the best!"

The nice lady smiled and said, "You are very welcome. I'm glad you like Lily. She is a very special doll. She loves you very much. Take good care of her." Anna and Mommy hugged the nice lady and said, "Thank you, thank you, thank you!" They took Lily and went home. Anna and Lily played together and had a lot of fun. They were best friends again.
<|end|>


