Lily and Ben were playing in the garden. They liked to pretend they were space explorers, looking for new planets and stars. They had a big cardboard box that they used as their spaceship. They painted it with bright colors and drew windows and buttons on it.

One day, they decided to go on a very long and tough mission. They packed some snacks and toys in their spaceship and got ready to blast off. "Are you ready, Ben?" Lily asked. "Yes, I am, Lily," Ben said. "Let's lock the door so no one can get in." They closed the flap of the box and pretended to lock it with a key.

They made loud noises as they flew through the sky. They saw clouds and birds and planes. They imagined they were passing by the moon and the sun and many stars. They wanted to find a star that was very special and shiny. They looked and looked, but they could not see one.

They started to feel hungry and tired. They opened their snacks and ate them. They played with their toys for a little while. They missed their mom and dad. They wondered if they would ever find their star. They felt sad and lonely.

Then, they heard a knock on the door of their spaceship. They were surprised and scared. Who could it be? They unlocked the door and opened it. They saw their mom and dad smiling at them. They had come to look for them and bring them inside. They had a big cake with candles on it. They said, "Happy birthday, Lily and Ben! We have a surprise for you. Look up at the sky. Do you see that star? That's your star. We named it after you. It's the Lily and Ben star. It's very special and shiny, just like you."

Lily and Ben were so happy. They hugged their mom and dad. They thanked them for the cake and the star. They said, "We love you, mom and dad. You are the best. And we love our star. It's the best star ever." They blew out the candles and made a wish. They wished they could always be space explorers and have fun adventures. But they also wished they could always come back to their home and their family. They knew they had everything they needed. They were very lucky.
<|end|>


