<|asst|>
Anna and Ben were playing with their toys in the living room. They liked to pretend they were in a different world, where they could do anything they wanted. They had a big box that they used as a door to their world.

"Let's enter our world and have some fun!" Ben said. He picked up his toy sword and his hat. "I'm a brave knight, and you're a princess."

Anna nodded and grabbed her doll and her crown. "I'm a princess, and you're my knight. Let's go!" She followed Ben to the box and crawled inside.

Inside the box, they saw a lot of colorful pictures that they had drawn and stuck on the walls. They had a castle, a forest, a dragon, and a treasure. They smiled and started to play.

But then, they heard a loud noise outside the box. It was their big brother, Tom. He was angry because he wanted to watch TV, and they were making too much noise.

"Hey, you two, get out of my way!" Tom shouted. He kicked the box and made it fall over. Anna and Ben screamed and fell out of the box. Their toys and pictures were scattered on the floor.

"Tom, you're mean!" Anna cried. She hugged her doll and her crown.

"Tom, you're bad!" Ben yelled. He waved his sword and his hat.

Tom laughed and walked to the TV. He turned it on and ignored them.

Anna and Ben were sad and angry. They looked at their ruined world and felt like crying. But then, they had an idea. They got up and ran to their room. They took another box and some more paper and crayons. They decided to make a new world, where Tom could not enter. They worked hard and made it even better than before. They smiled and crawled inside.

"Let's enter our world and have some fun!" Anna said. She picked up her doll and her crown. "I'm a princess, and you're my knight."

"Let's go!" Ben said. He picked up his sword and his hat. "I'm a brave knight, and you're a princess."

They played happily in their new world, and forgot about Tom and his TV. They had each other, and that was enough.
<|end|>


