<|asst|>
Lily and Ben are friends. They like to play in the park. One day, they see a big slide. Lily wants to go first. She runs to the slide and climbs up. Ben follows her.

"Wait for me, Lily!" Ben calls. "We can slide together!"

But Lily does not wait. She slides down very fast. She laughs and feels good. Ben is sad. He wanted to slide with Lily.

Lily sees Ben's face. She knows she did not do a good thing. She says sorry to Ben.

"Sorry, Ben. I was too fast. Do you want to slide again with me?" Lily asks.

Ben nods. He is not mad at Lily. He knows she tells the truth. He climbs up the slide with Lily. They hold hands and slide down together. They laugh and feel good.

They are friends again.
<|end|>


