<|asst|>
Once upon a time, there was a prince and a princess who wanted to get married. So they went to the market and bought a big, sparkly diamond. The diamond was so beautiful and fit perfectly on the princess's finger. The prince and princess looked at each other and smiled. They were so happy. On the day of the wedding, the princess wore a beautiful dress and the prince wore a sharp suit. Everyone cheered when they said 'I do' and married each other. As the sun set over the castle, they sealed the marriage with a kiss and their diamond sparkled. The prince and princess were so happy they married each other!
<|end|>


