Once upon a time there was a friendly bear. He liked to explore and have adventures. 
One day he decided to go on a walk in the woods. He was walking along when he stumbled across an old shoe! 
The bear was very curious. He picked it up and said, "What a strange shoe! I wonder what it is doing here."
He looked around and saw a dark, scary cave. The bear began to feel scared. 
Suddenly he heard a voice. The bear shouted, "Who's there?" 
"It's me!" Said a small creature. "Don't be scared, I'm friendly!" 
The friendly creature was a frog. The frog said, "I ended up here when I was playing with my shoe!"
The bear and the frog quickly became friends. From then on, they always watched out for each other and went on many adventures.
<|end|>


