Johnny was a young boy, and he had a modest heart. He loved to go on adventures and explore. One day, Johnny was running through the park and he slipped on a rock. He fell and he was scared. But he was brave and he stood back up and kept on running. He saw a beautiful flower in the grass and he took it in his hands. He put it in his pocket and continued on. He heard a faint sound in the far away sky, and it sounded like music. Johnny followed the tune and it brought him to the edge of a lake. It was so lovely and peaceful. He slipped off his shoes and dipped his feet in the warm water. He felt very content, and Johnny knew he'd keep the lake's gentle music in his heart forever.
<|end|>


