<|asst|>
James was a brave knight who was guarding his castle. He always held his shield tightly and kept a close eye on his kingdom. One day, James was strolling the gates when he saw something unexpected. He spotted an evil dragon that was lurking outside the castle walls. James immediately grabbed his shield and prepared for battle.

The dragon roared and opened its monstrous jaws. James stepped up bravely and stared the dragon down. He knew he was the only thing standing between the dragon and his kingdom. Suddenly, the dragon shot out a powerful blast of fire. James tried his best to protect himself and the castle, but his shield was no match for the dragon.

James was frustrated and scared. He knew he had to do something, but he didn't know what to do. He stared at the dragon, looking for some way to protect his kingdom. In the end, the dragon was too powerful and James was badly burned. The castle was destroyed and the dragon flew away, victorious.
<|end|>


<|sys|>
