Once there was a boy named Tom. Tom lived in a small house with his family.

It was almost spring, and Tom was really excited. He wanted to go outside and play in the sunshine and flowers. 

But when spring arrived, Tom was sad. His family was angry and he didn't know why. He asked them what was wrong, but they just shook their heads and said nothing. 

Tom was confused. He felt scared, so he just stayed inside. 

But then something amazing happened. One day, his family started to get happy again. Tom asked why and his mom told him that the warm, sunny days of spring had made them happy. 

Tom was so excited. He finally understood why spring was so special and he knew he would never feel scared or angry again when spring arrived.
