Once there was a man and his wife. The man was always grumpy and mean.

One day, the wife decided to go for a walk.

"Don't go," the man said, "it's too dangerous."

But the wife went anyway.

When she came back, the man noticed that she had something ugly around her neck. He got very angry and yelled at her.

"Where did you get that ugly thing?" he demanded.

The wife didn't want to tell him the truth, so she said nothing.

Suddenly, the man got so mad that he grabbed the ugly thing off his wife's neck and threw it away.

The man and his wife had a very bad ending. And the ugly thing was never seen again.
