Once upon a time, there lived a little girl called Amy. She was only three years old and lived in a small cottage.

One day, Amy was playing in the garden of her cottage. Suddenly, she saw a pile of grey ash. She felt a bit scared and curious at the same time. She decided to go near it to explore.

When Amy got close, she heard a voice coming from the ash. It said, "Help me." It was a magical fairy called Sam. She had an accident and now she was stuck in the ash. She looked very hurt.

