Once upon a time there was a cub. Every day, the cub liked to go outside and rub his cheeks on the bark of a big tree. 
One day, the cub looked up and saw a wild plane in the sky. It was so big, the cub was so excited! He stopped what he was doing and watched the plane fly far away. 
The cub wanted to fly just like the plane. He started to rub his paws on the tree and imagined a wish. He closed his eyes and made a wish. 
The next day, the cub heard a strange sound. It was louder and louder! The cub was very curious and went to investigate. As he got closer, he saw the wild plane coming towards him. The cub was so scared but he could not move. Suddenly, the plane crashed into the tree and the cub was no more.
<|end|>


