Once there was a bird who wanted to travel around the world. He had two wings so he decided to sail in the sky. He asked all of the other birds to join him, but they refused and said they did not believe in his dream.

The bird was so sad, but he refused to give up. He decided to fly alone. He made sure to be honest and followed the wind to reach his goal.

The bird flew for many days and he was almost there. But then he encountered a strong gust of wind that was too strong for his wings. The wind pushed his wings back and the bird fell into the sea.

The bird tried to swim back to shore but he was too tired. He eventually lost his strength and sank to the bottom of the sea and was never seen again.
<|end|>


