Anna was so excited. She was going to the zoo for the first time. She had heard so many stories about it! Anna looked around at all the animals she had only seen in pictures. She stopped to gaze at the lions. They were so strong and majestic. 

Suddenly, Anna made a new friend. His name was Ben and he was a famous zookeeper. Ben loved to talk about the animals at the zoo. He shared his opinion about each one of them. 

Anna loved to hear Ben talk. She asked him a lot of questions and he answered them all. His opinion made the animals seem even more special. 

At the end of the day, Anna waved goodbye to Ben. She was so happy to have met a famous zookeeper. She had learned so much from him and she couldn't wait to go back to the zoo again.
<|end|>


