One day, a young boy named Tom went out to play hockey with his friends. Tom was so excited to play and make new friends, but suddenly he started to panic. He saw a naughty big dog running around in circles, getting closer to him and his friends.

Tom's friends were scared. They all shouted, "What do we do? We need help!"

Tom took a deep breath and shouted, "Let's all run back to the house!"

Tom and his friends started to panic, but then suddenly the naughty dog stopped running so they all took off running back to the house.

Tom was so relieved when he made it back to the house safe and sound. Although he was upset he didn't get to play hockey with his friends, he was happy that he was able to save them all from the big naughty dog.
<|end|>


