Once upon a time, there was a helpful girl named Lily. Lily liked to pretend every day. She especially loved pretending to be a princess in her favourite white dress. 

One day after school, Lily was playing in her favourite room. She put on her white dress and was pretending it was a special day for her. She heard a sound outside.

Lily said, "Who's there?"

A mean and scary man answered, "I am."

Lily became scared and tried to run away, but the man blocked the door. He grabbed Lily and dragged her away to a dark place. 

Lily was never seen again. She had been taken away by a bad man and nobody was ever able to help her.
<|end|>


