John was feeling thoughtful as he lined up in the store. He had been waiting here for some time, but he was the last to enter. Everyone else was in the line ahead of him. As he waited, John could feel his patience wearing thin. Suddenly, a voice called out from the back of the line. It was a security guard who had caught John trying to sneak in without paying! John was very embarrassed and upset. The security guard told everyone in the line that John had been trying to cheat them all. Before John knew what was happening, the guard grabbed him and dragged him away. John had never felt so embarrassed and ashamed. He never wanted to try something like this again.
<|end|>


