Once there was a little boy named Tom. He loved to play with his dogs and do other fun things. One day, Tom heard about a special band that would come to his town. He was so excited that he just had to go see them.

When Tom got to the band's concert, something strange happened. He noticed that their shirts were all white. He had never seen a band wear all white before and wondered what it meant.

That night when Tom went to bed, he had the strangest dreams. In the dreams, the band was printing something special. When Tom awoke in the morning, he couldn't help but think that maybe something cool was going to happen at the band's next concert.

The next day, Tom was at the band's concert again. Just like before, all the band members were wearing white. But this time, there was something different. At the end of the concert, the band started printing out special pieces of paper that said "Tom is the coolest kid ever!" 

Tom was so excited to find out that the white shirts that the band was wearing meant that they were planning a special surprise just for him! He was the happiest boy in the world.
<|end|>


