Once upon a time there was a little girl named Jane. Jane loved to play outdoors and often spent days in the sun playing on the ground. Every day she would explore looking for something new and original.

One day, she found the most wonderful thing ever. She found a big, juicy rose! She plucked it from the ground and hugged it close to show it to her mom.

"Oh! What a beautiful flower!" her mom said, "But it needs a kiss!"

So Jane kissed the flower and suddenly it started to sparkle. Moments later she saw the most amazing sight. A rainbow colored butterfly had emerged from the rose!

The butterfly flew away and Jane was amazed. She was so happy with her original discovery!
