Once upon a time, there was a cute goose. The goose liked to swim in the cool pond.
One day, the goose saw a curious floating thing in the pond. He went closer to take a look.
Suddenly, it shrank! The goose was very surprised and said, "Wow! That's so cool!"
The goose was very excited and he tried to touch it but when he got closer, the thing shrank again!
The goose thought this was so funny, he tried to touch it again and again. Each time, it shrank!
The goose laughed and laughed until the sun started to set. Then, the goose swam back home.
