One day, John wanted to have some fun. He decided to climb a big tree in the backyard. He took big steps up the tree and soon he reached the top. He was glad to be up high.

John enjoyed looking around and spotted a little round door in the tree. He tried to open it but it was stuck. Then he noticed a sign that said "Turn to open." He grabbed the handle and gave it a strong turn. To his surprise, the door opened and a bright light shone out.

John stepped through the door and was amazed! A big slide had been set up inside the treehouse. He was so glad he had the chance to climb the tree and turn the door handle. He slid all the way down and laughed with joy!
