Once upon a time there was a gifted little girl. She loved movies and always went to special movie showings. One day, when the little girl went to the movie theater, something went wrong and the theater began to burn. The little girl quickly ran out of the theater.

The firemen came to put out the fire. They worked really hard and soon the fire was gone. Everybody thanked the firemen for saving the theater.

The little girl was thankful that no one was hurt. She was surprised that the movie was still playing. She watched it and enjoyed the show very much.

At the end of the movie, the entire audience applauded the movie and the little girl. They all agreed that she was very gifted.
