Once upon a time there was a young girl. She walked through the forest and saw a big tree. She decided to climb it and when she got to the top, she saw a magical wrap. It floated in the air and she watched it turn around and around. She reached out and grabbed it in her hands. The wrap sparkled so brightly and it felt very special. 

Suddenly, something amazing happened. The wrap started to change shape and shrink until it was small enough for the young girl to put into her pocket. She decided to take the wrap home.

Back at home, the young girl opened the wrap and showed it to her mom and dad. Her eyes lit up as she explained what happened in the forest. Her parents were very amazed and happy. They hugged her and they all turned the wrap together. When they turned it, they saw something incredible - inside was a special surprise just for her. 

The young girl was so happy that she had found the magical wrap. She held it close and knew it would stay special to her forever.
