Once there was a little girl who loved to play outside. One day, she discovered a mysterious lawn that she had never seen before. She decided to explore it. As she stepped onto the lawn, she felt something strange. Suddenly, the grass began to stand up on its own! The little girl was scared and tried to run away. But no matter how fast she ran, the tall grass kept following her.

The little girl didn't know what to do. She desperately wanted to make the grass stop. Then she got an idea. She decided to try singing a song. As soon as she started singing, the grass began to calm down and eventually lay back flat on the ground.

The little girl was relieved and she learned an important lesson that day. Sometimes, even mysterious things can be overcome when you use your voice.
<|end|>


