Once upon a time, there was a happy little bunny called Jack. Every day, Jack would follow the path through the meadow to find the most comfortable pillow in the world.

Jack was determined to find the most comfortable place to take a nap. One day, he wandered too far and got lost. He looked around but there was no path to follow and soon it got dark.

Jack was afraid and started to cry. He searched and searched until he found the most comfortable pillow. He was so happy! He snuggled into the pillow and fell asleep.

But when morning came, Jack had a big surprise. The pillow was actually an angry badger's bed! The badger was very angry and growled at Jack. He ran away as fast as he could, but never found his way back home.

Jack had a very bad ending to his adventure. He was never seen again.
<|end|>


