Once upon a time there was a little girl. She was three years old and really loved going to the zoo. Every day she would go to the zoo and poke the different animals with a stick - but very gently!

The animals at the zoo were very nice to her and always let her poke them. The giraffe was especially gentle and the little girl was very grateful.

One day the little girl realized that she had poked all the animals in the zoo at least once. She was very happy and felt proud of herself.

From then on, whenever the little girl visited the zoo she was always very gentle with the animals and always made sure to give them a friendly poke!
