Once upon a time there was a little girl called Emily. Emily had a very special dream - to own her own doggy. Every day, Emily would look out of the window to see if there was any doggy that wanted to be her friend.

One day, Emily saw a doggy walking up and down the street. She opened the window and shouted out to the doggy, asking him to come and stay with her. The doggy barked and ran towards the window. 

Emily was so excited that the doggy wanted to be her own. She opened the door and the doggy marched inside. Emily named the doggy 'Rover' and they had lots of fun playing together each day. 

But one day, Emily woke up to find Rover laying dead in her bedroom. She cried and cried. All her doggy dreams were dead, just like Rover! Emily was very sad. 

Even though she was sad, Emily still remembered the happy times that she and Rover had spent together. She decided to remember the good times and keep dreaming of having her own doggy once again.
