Once upon a time, there was a hidden crown. Nobody knew where it was, but it was there. One day, a brave prince decided he would try to find this hidden crown. He looked everywhere, high and low, but he just couldn't find it.

Finally, he found it in a secret cave. He was so happy! He grabbed the crown and cut off a tiny piece. As he was about to take it away, a magic bird flew down and said, "Now you have the crown, your wish will come true!"

The prince wished for good luck, and the magic bird granted it. Now the prince had a new crown, and all his wishes would come true. He was so happy he wanted to share his luck with the world! He went off and told everyone about his hidden crown and the magic inside it.

And they all lived happily ever after.
<|end|>


