Bella was a little girl. She was three years old and she loved adventures. One day, she decided to explore her garden. 

She saw a tall tree. She wanted to climb it and see what was on top. She started to climb and suddenly, she saw something shining. It was a big, shiny apple! 

Bella was happy and she wanted to try it. She picked the apple and took a bite. It was sour! She made a sour face and showed it to her mom. 

Her mom smiled and said: "We can make something delicious out of that! I'm going to show you how!" 

So, mom and Bella went to the kitchen. Together, they cut the sour apple into small pieces and put them in a pan. She added some sugar and spices and cooked it until it was ready. Now, it was a tasty, sweet food. 

Bella was so happy. She ate the delicious food and thanked her mom for showing her how to turn something sour into something sweet.
<|end|>


