One day, a girl went to see the barn. She was so excited to explore. She saw a big, red barn and thought it was so pretty. When she went inside, it was so soft. She noticed a big pile of hay in the corner, so she decided to sit down and take a closer look.

When she was sitting in the hay, suddenly she heard a noise. She looked around and there was a bunny! It was so cute. The bunny hopped around the barn and the girl smiled. She slowly moved closer to the bunny and pet its soft fur.

The girl was so happy that she had seen the bunny in the barn. She said goodbye to the bunny and then left to go home. But from that day, she kept coming back to the barn to see if the bunny was still there.
<|end|>


