Once upon a time, there was a little boy who loved tomatoes. He went to pick some tomatoes in the garden everyday, because they were so yummy!

One morning he spotted a huge tomato. He smiled and started to slip towards it, but he was too excited and he slipped over. He began to cry - the huge tomato was ruined!

"It's ok, my little one," his mum said. "Let's go get another tomato".

So the little boy and his mum went to find another tomato, but none were as big or as yummy as the huge one. They had to go home empty handed.

The little boy was so sad. He had wanted that huge tomato so badly. He didn't like the ending at all.
<|end|>


