Once upon a time there was a poor family living in a small village. Every day, the mother and father tried to make ends meet but it was always difficult for them.

One day, the mother said to the father, "I have an idea. Let's put together a team to help us out."

The father was a bit hesitant and said "But who will help us? We're so poor and no one is rich to help us for free."

The mother said, "Let's ask all the neighbors if they will marry us. That way, all the families can join and help each other out."

The father agreed and they asked all the neighbors. To their surprise, they all agreed and the team of families was formed. From then on, all the families worked together and helped each other with whatever was needed. 

This way, the poor family was able to make ends meet and live happily ever after.
<|end|>


