Once upon a time there was a family of bunnies. They loved to organize things in their home. One day, they decided to organize the cushion they used to sit on in the corner of the room. They chose some very soft and comfy cushions and they made sure they were arranged in a nice way.

Next, the bunnies got to work making some tasty snacks. They made some yummy sandwiches and some crunchy carrot sticks. They were very excited to enjoy their snacks on the freshly organized cushions.

When everything was ready, the bunnies hopped over to the corner of the room. They snuggled up on the soft cushions and enjoyed the tasty snacks. The little bunnies were very happy with their snacks and their cozy cushions!
