Once upon a time, there was a lazy fairy who lived high in the sky. Every day she would float around, never doing much. 
Until one day, she noticed a door that had been locked from the outside. The fairy was curious, so she tried to unlock it. 
But it was too hard for the fairy to open, no matter how hard she tried. She flew away feeling very unhappy. 
The next day, the fairy returned and found a little girl standing near the door. The girl had a tiny key in her hand and was trying to unlock the door. 
The fairy watched as the little girl managed to unlock the door. When the door opened, there was a magical world inside. 
The lazy fairy was so happy to see the magical world, but she was sad she had not been able to unlock it herself! She thanked the little girl and they became friends.

From then on, the lazy fairy and the little girl explored the magical world together. They had many wonderful adventures and the lazy fairy was no longer lazy!
<|end|>


