One day a man built a trap next to a pond. He hoped to catch something that he could eat. He waited patiently but nothing happened. Then he decided to twist the trap in a special way. He thought this would help him catch something.

Suddenly he heard a noise. He was so excited. He looked into the trap to see what he had caught. It was a very difficult animal. It was so strong that it was impossible to open the trap! The man tried and tried to open it but it was impossible.

The man was so frustrated. He started to cry when he heard a voice. It said, "Please help me! I'm stuck in this trap!" The man was so surprised. He realised that he had trapped a little boy!

He tried and tried to open the trap, but it was impossible. The man had to go away, feeling very ashamed and sad. The little boy was trapped there and no one could save him.
