Once upon a time, there was a girl called Anna. She loved trying out new tastes. One day, her mom gave her something to try. It was called butter. Anna was so excited to try it. She put some on her finger and tasted it. It was so tasty!

Anna loved butter so much, she asked her mom to buy her some more. Her mom bought her a jar of butter. Anna smiled and opened it. She tasted the butter and it was so yummy!

Anna shared the butter with everyone in the family. Everyone loved the tasty butter. Anna was so happy because she loved making everyone smile with butter. From that day on, Anna always asked for butter whenever she wanted to try something new.
