Once upon a time there was a doggy called Spot. Spot was a very lovely pooch and he always tried to behave. Spot would play in the garden every day and he loved to run around and explore his surroundings. One day, Spot decided to investigate some far away bushes. When he got there he found a lovely surprise, a basket filled with yummy treats! Spot was so excited that he forgot to behave and started to bark and run around in circles. Thankfully his owner saw him and ran over to him, giving him lots of cuddles and love. Spot was so happy, he wagged his tail and snuggled up to his owner. From then on, he always tried to be extra good and behave, but he never forgot the lovely surprise he found that day.
