The place was full of pretty colors and smelled like fresh flowers. Piper felt like she was in a dream. She looked around and saw butterflies flying all around. She wanted to stay forever in this amazing place.

Piper said goodbye to the magical place and headed home. She knew that Bear had sent her to the best place ever and she felt so lucky!
<|end|>


