Once upon a time, there was a big, round planet in the sky. It was very busy, always spinning, rolling and moving. Everyone on it had lots to do.

One day, a little boy named Joe decided he wanted to get on the planet. He didn't know how, though - until he had an amazing idea! He got a big bouncy ball and started rolling it along the ground. As the ball rolled, it got bigger and bigger. Soon enough, Joe rolled himself up in the ball and before he knew it, he was on the planet.

Joe was amazed! Everywhere he looked was something new. He saw people and animals, trees, rivers and more. Joe had lots of fun exploring the planet - it was so exciting!

Eventually, it was time to leave. Joe waved goodbye and rolled off the planet. He rolled and rolled until he reached home. Joe was so happy to have seen the busy planet.
