Once upon a time, there was a little girl. She had a special dress that she loved to wear. One day, something very ugly came to her house. It made the little girl very scared. She ran to her special dress and put it on.

The ugly thing came closer and closer. The little girl started to cry. She asked it what it wanted, but the thing just kept coming. Suddenly, it grabbed the dress from her. The little girl was so scared that she ran away and hid.

The little girl was very sad. She had lost her special dress. She learned that it's not okay to trust ugly things.

Moral of the story: Don't trust ugly things.
