They all went out to the park and had a wonderful time. They laughed and ate delicious food and played games.

But then the wind blew and made a lot of dust. Daisy was worried that the dust would ruin the picnic.

But then something amazing happened. Daisy waved her arms and the dust disappeared. Everyone was so impressed. Daisy had saved the picnic! 

Everyone cheered and thanked Daisy for the amazing picnic. She had made new friends and made sure the picnic was a success.
