Once upon a time there was a small and adorable bird. The bird liked to fly around the sky, near the clouds. Everywhere it flew, it left a special symbol. 

The bird flew to the park and found some children playing. They were so excited when they saw the bird and followed it around, watching it fly. 

The bird flew to a tree and perched on a branch. The children smiled as they watched the bird enjoying its freedom in the sky. 

Suddenly, the bird spotted a large worm on the ground and quickly flew down to get it! The children laughed as they watched the adorable bird fly around. 

The bird ate its yummy treat, then flew away slowly into the sky, leaving the shiny symbol behind. The children waved goodbye as the bird flew off,until it was just a tiny speck in the sky.
