Once upon a time, there was a little boy named John. He had a very special mission. He wanted to get to the top of the castle. Everyone said it was impossible and the castle was very high. But John had a plan.

One day, he knelt down and asked for help from the magical stars in the sky. Then he stood up and began to march. He went up one step at a time, and slowly, the castle began to get closer.

The castle was so high and John was getting tired, but he kept going. He knew he could do it. After climbing up all the steps, he finally reached the top of the castle.

John looked around and all his hard work had paid off, he had made it to the top. He had climbed the high castle and proved everyone wrong. They all thought it was impossible, but John showed that it could be done.
