Once upon a time, there was a fit man who was in a bad mood. He drove in his car to the city, but there was too much traffic. He got very angry and started to yell. Suddenly, he had an idea. He wanted to deliver something special to the city! He took out a big package from his car and placed it in the city. Suddenly, everyone started to run away, even the traffic. Then, the fit man ran away and the package exploded. It was very sad, as everything got destroyed. Sadly, the fit man never delivered his package.
