Once upon a time there was a girl named Amy. She lived with her mom and dad and they were very nice to her. One day, while Amy was playing in the park, she heard a noise. It seemed like a message in the sky.

She looked up and couldn't believe her eyes. There was a big bunny in the sky flying around. It was like a regular old bunny, but it was in the sky. 

Amy was so excited she shouted for her mom and dad to come and see. When they saw the bunny, they were as surprised as Amy. 

"What do you think the message is?" Amy asked her mom and dad. 

"Maybe it's a sign from above," Mom said. "Let's just keep watching and see if it does anything else."

So, they watched the bunny fly around in the sky until the sun went down. Then, just as the sky was getting dark, the bunny flew away. 

Even though they never figured out what the message was, Amy and her family agreed it was a magical experience. They all went home smiling.
<|end|>


