Once upon a time, there were two friends named Jane and Jack. They had lots of fun playing together each day.

One day, as they were playing, Jane noticed something yellow and sparkly on the ground. She picked it up and showed it to Jack.

Jack said, "Wow! What is it?"

Jane said, "I don't know, but it's so pretty!"

Jack thought for a minute, then said, "I think it's a match!"

Jane said, "How do you know?" 

Jack said, "It looks like a welcome sign my mom has on her door. It has the same yellow and sparkly colors and it says 'Welcome' at the top."

Just then, their nosy neighbor poked her head out of her window and said, "Hey kids! What are you doing over there?"

Jane and Jack smiled and said, "We found a match!" before quickly running away.
