"It's not worth the price," said another.

The villagers didn't know what to do. Then, a wise old man stepped in. He said, "I can help you make a better robot. It will be strong and cheap!"

The villagers got to work and soon, they had a better robot. This time it was cheap and strong. The villagers smiled as the robot began to unite them.

