When Sam reached the river, he walked around the thick water. All of a sudden, he saw something shiny in the water and wanted to get it out.

"Maybe I can climb down there," he thought.

Sam started to climb in, but he slipped and dropped into the river! 

Mommy heard the splash and ran to the river. She couldn't find Sam because the water was so thick. She screamed for him but it was too late.

Sam had gone under the water. He never came back up. 

The end.
