Once upon a time there was a little girl called Bella. She was very curious and loved to explore everything around her.

One day she saw a tall screen outside in the garden. It was so delicate that she wanted to touch it to see if it was real. She carefully leaned up against the screen with her hand outstretched.

Suddenly, Bella heard a voice behind her. 
"Be very careful, Bella! That screen is very delicate," said the voice.

Bella turned around and saw her big brother, Ryan, standing there. 
"Don't worry, I am being careful!" said Bella, smiling brightly. 

Ryan smiled back and said, "ok, just be careful and don't lean too hard!" 

From then on, every time Bella looked at the screen, she was very gentle and careful when she leaned against it.
<|end|>


