One day, a young girl named Liz was playing in her backyard. She was wearing a pretty leather jacket, and a hat on her head. She was very grateful for these clothes because they kept her warm.

Liz started jumping around, having lots of fun. Suddenly, she sneezed! She sneezed so hard, her hat almost flew off her head!

Liz looked around, and she saw her mother. Her mother had a huge smile on her face. She was so proud of Liz for sneezing. In fact, she gave Liz a big hug!

Liz felt very grateful to have a mother who loves her. She gave her mum a big hug back and thanked her for the leather jacket and hat that kept her warm. 

The mother and daughter shared a happy moment together. Suddenly, Liz sneezed again! She giggle and her mum gave her another big hug. Liz smiled, happy to be loved.
<|end|>


