Once upon a time, there was a little girl. She wanted to build something very special. She had an amazing idea. All she needed was steam.

She decided to make a big pot of water and build a fire underneath it. The fire was big and strong. Unfortunately, it was too heavy for the little girl to lift.

Suddenly, a big steam cloud burst from the pot. The little girl was so excited! She had made steam and it was just perfect for her big project.

Using the steam, she built a beautiful castle made of paper, wood and leaves. It was the most amazing castle anyone had ever seen.

The little girl was now so proud of herself. She had made something really special, all with her own steam.
<|end|>


