One day, there was a hunter walking through the forest. He had been searching all day for something, but he couldn't find it. Just then, he heard a voice.

"Can I help you?" asked the voice.

The hunter looked up to see a small girl, only 3 years old, standing in front of him. She was smiling, with a very impressive look in her eye.

The hunter was amazed. "Yes, please," he said. "I've been looking for something all day, but I can't find it."

The girl smiled again. "I can solve this," she said. "Follow me."

The hunter followed the girl through the forest. They searched through trees and bushes, and eventually found the item the hunter was looking for.

The young girl was impressive! She had solved the hunter's problem so quickly. She smiled and waved goodbye as the hunter thanked her for her help.
<|end|>


