Once there was a boy who was walking on the road. He wanted to get home but he couldn't find it. He kept on walking for hours. He got so tired that he decided to take a rest.

Suddenly, he found a big sign on the road. It was his home! He was so happy that he thanked the sign.

He started runing towards his home but he saw a foolish dog in the middle of the road. The boy had to stop so he said thank you to the dog for not blocking the road.

Then the boy arrived at his home. He was very happy and thanked God for helping him find his way.
