Once upon a time there was a nosy cat. Every day the cat liked to move around the garden, sniffing everything and watching the other animals.

One day, the cat was walking past a small pond and stopped to look at the fish. Suddenly a frog hopped up to the cat and said, "Hi! What is your name?"

The cat was very surprised, but it told the frog, "My name is Cat."

The frog nodded and said, "That's a nice name! I'm going to move around the garden. Do you want to come with me?"

The nosy cat nodded and the two animals started to move around the garden together. They chatted and laughed while they moved around the garden, sniffing the flowers and bushes.

At the end of the day, the two friends said goodbye and promised to meet again soon.
<|end|>


