Jake had a busy day. He was busy lifting things. Suddenly, he heard a noise. He looked around and saw a small rail. Jake went to it and tried to lift it with all his might, but it was too heavy. 

"I can't lift it all by myself," he said sadly. He looked around and saw a few people nearby.

"Can you help me lift this rail?" he asked. 

One of the people smiled. "Yes, of course we can help you," they said.

Soon, they all worked together and managed to lift the rail. Jake was so happy! They put the rail down and Jake gave them a big thank-you hug. 

The people smiled and said goodbye. Jake went home feeling happy and satisfied from all the busy work he had done.
<|end|>


