Once upon a time there was a little girl. She was 3 years old. She was walking through the park.

Suddenly, she saw something unusual! It was a pair of scissors. The girl liked scissors, so she went to take a closer look.

Suddenly, the scissors started to yell! The little girl was scared. She jumped back and ran.

She ran all the way home. When she got there, she told her mom about the unusual yelling scissors. Mom laughed and said it was probably just the wind in the trees!

The little girl was relieved. It was nice to know that the unusual yelling scissors wasn't something to be scared of!
<|end|>


