They decide to keep the crystal and take it to their room. They put it on their shelf and look at it every day. They like to imagine what the crystal can do. Sometimes they think it can make wishes come true. Sometimes they think it can talk to them. Sometimes they think it can glow in the dark.

They are happy with their crystal. They think it is the best thing they ever found in the garden. They feel lucky and curious and proud. They love their crystal.
