<|asst|>
Lily and Ben were hungry. They wanted to eat a sandwich. Mom said she would make them a sandwich, but they had to wait. Lily and Ben tried to be patient, but they were very hungry.

"Mom, is the sandwich ready?" Lily asked.

"Not yet, sweetie. I have to cut the bread and the cheese and the ham. Can you help me?" Mom said.

"Yes, Mom. I can help you. Ben, can you help too?" Lily said.

Ben nodded. He liked to help Mom. He and Lily went to the kitchen. Mom gave them a knife and a plate. They cut the bread and the cheese and the ham. They put them on the plate.

"Good job, Lily and Ben. Now we can make the sandwich. Do you want to put the cheese and the ham on the bread?" Mom said.

"Yes, Mom. I want to put the cheese. Ben, do you want to put the ham?" Lily said.

"Yes, Lily. I want to put the ham. I like ham." Ben said.

They put the cheese and the ham on the bread. Mom put another bread on top. She cut the sandwich in half. She gave one half to Lily and one half to Ben.

"Here you go, Lily and Ben. Your sandwich is ready. Enjoy!" Mom said.

"Thank you, Mom. You are the best. The sandwich looks yummy." Lily said.

"Thank you, Mom. You are the best. The sandwich smells good." Ben said.

They took a big bite of the sandwich. They smiled. They were happy. The sandwich was delicious.

Suddenly, a cat appeared. It jumped on the table. It wanted the sandwich too. It tried to grab the sandwich from Lily and Ben.

"Hey, cat. Go away. This is our sandwich. You can't have it." Lily said.

"Hey, cat. Go away. This is our sandwich. You can't have it." Ben said.

They waved their hands at the cat. The cat hissed. It ran away. It was scared.

Lily and Ben laughed. They finished their sandwich. They hugged Mom.

"Mom, we love you. And we love your sandwich." Lily said.

"Mom, we love you. And we love your sandwich." Ben said.

Mom smiled. She hugged them back.

"I love you too, Lily and Ben. And I'm proud of you. You were very patient and helpful." Mom said.

They were a happy family. They liked to eat sandwiches. And they liked to chase cats.
<|end|>


