Once upon a time, there was a little bunny named Fluffy. Fluffy loved to play outside in the sun and eat carrots. One day, Fluffy's friend, a little bird named Tweet, flew down to say hello.

"Hi Fluffy! What are you doing?" asked Tweet.

"I'm just soaking up the sun and munching on some carrots," said Fluffy.

Tweet looked up at the sky and noticed the light was getting dimmer. "Uh oh, it looks like it's going to rain soon. You better go inside before you get wet and your fur gets all soft."

Fluffy hopped into his burrow just in time before the rain started pouring down. But the rain was too strong and the burrow started to fill with water. Fluffy tried to swim to safety, but he couldn't escape. Sadly, Fluffy drowned in the flood and his friend Tweet never saw him again. The end.
