Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Lily. She loved to draw with her pencil. One day, she was drawing a picture of her family when she accidentally dropped her pencil on the floor. It was very hot outside, and the pencil rolled under the couch where it was even hotter. 

Lily tried to reach for her pencil, but she couldn't. So, she went to her mom and asked for help. Her mom tried to get the pencil, but she couldn't reach it either. They decided to wait until it cooled down outside before trying again. 

Later that day, Lily's dad came home from work. He sat down on the couch and accidentally sat on the pencil. It hurt him very badly. They had to go to the hospital to get it taken out. Lily felt very sad that her dad got hurt because of her pencil. She wished she had printed her picture without it.
<|end|>


