Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Lily. She was walking with her mommy when they saw a big sign. The sign said, "Tie your shoes before crossing the street." 

Lily's mommy said, "Lily, your shoes are untied. Can you tie them?" 

Lily was nervous because she had never tied her shoes before. She said, "Mommy, I don't know how to tie my shoes." 

Her mommy said, "Don't worry, I'll teach you." And she showed Lily how to tie her shoes. Lily was so happy that she learned something new!
<|end|>


