Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Lily. One day, she went to the park with her mommy. They saw a big bird fly in the sky. Lily said, "Look, mommy! A bird!" Her mommy said, "Yes, Lily. That's a bird. It's flying high." 

Then, they walked to the playground. Lily saw an empty swing. She said, "Mommy, can I swing?" Her mommy said, "Sure, Lily. You can swing." So, Lily sat on the swing and started swinging back and forth. 

After a while, Lily saw a bug on the ground. She said, "Mommy, what's that bug?" Her mommy said, "Let's examine it, Lily. It's a little bug. It has six legs." Lily was happy to learn about the bug. It was a fun event at the park.
<|end|>


