The squirrel said, "That's a big job to do. Do you think you will succeed?" 

Jack said, "I will try my best and I believe I can succeed." 

With his sword in hand, Jack went to the dragon's lair. The dragon was very big and scary, but Jack was brave. He fought with all his might and finally, he succeeded in defeating the dragon. The villagers were very happy and they celebrated Jack's victory.
