Once upon a time, there was a shy little girl named Lily. She loved to play with her toys all day long. One day, her mommy and daddy had a big argument. They were fighting about what to order for dinner. Lily was scared and didn't know what to do. She wanted her mommy and daddy to be happy and not fight.

The next day, Lily's mommy and daddy told her they were getting married. Lily was happy and excited. She loved her mommy and daddy and wanted them to be together forever. But then, her daddy said he didn't want to get married anymore. Lily was sad and confused. She didn't understand why her daddy changed his mind.

Lily's mommy and daddy talked and talked. They realized that they still loved each other and wanted to be together. They decided to order pizza for dinner and have a family movie night. Lily was happy that her mommy and daddy were happy again. She knew that they loved each other and that was all that mattered.
<|end|>


