Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Lily. She had a black cat named Mittens who loved to play with her. One day, Lily went to the park and found a lost puppy. She decided to take the puppy home and asked her mom if they could keep it. Her mom said they needed to ask her dad first. When her dad came home, they asked him if they could keep the puppy. He said yes and Lily was so happy that her family accepted the puppy. 

The next day, Lily and Mittens were playing in the house when they heard a knock on the door. Lily ran to the door and opened it. It was her friend, Sarah. Sarah asked if she could come in and play with Lily and Mittens. Lily said yes and they all played together. They had so much fun that Sarah asked if she could come back the next day. Lily said yes and they all hugged goodbye. 

Lily was happy that her family accepted the puppy and that her friend Sarah came over to play. She went to bed that night with a smile on her face, knowing that she had a lot of people and pets who loved her.
