Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Lily. One day, Lily went to the park with her mom. They brought a sandwich for lunch. But when they opened the lunch box, they saw that the sandwich was gone! Lily's mom was sad and confused because she did not know where the sandwich went. It was unknown to them who took the sandwich. 

Lily and her mom looked around the park to find the sandwich. They asked other people if they saw someone take it, but nobody knew. Just when they were about to give up, they saw a little squirrel running away with the sandwich in its mouth! Lily and her mom laughed and were happy to find out who took the sandwich. They decided to share the sandwich with the squirrel and had a fun picnic together.
