Once upon a time, there was a silly dog named Spot. Spot loved to play with his ball. One day, Spot was playing with his ball in the park. He saw a big cat. The cat was very strong. Spot wanted to be strong too. He wanted to have big muscles like the cat.

Spot asked the cat, "How do I get big muscles like you?" The cat said, "You must play and run a lot." So, Spot played and ran every day. He was very happy. But one day, while playing, Spot lost his ball. He was very sad.

Spot looked for his ball everywhere, but he could not find it. He asked his friends to help him find the ball. They looked and looked, but they could not find it either. Then, Spot saw the big cat again. The cat said, "I found your ball, Spot!" Spot was so happy. He thanked the cat and they played together. Spot had big muscles now, just like the cat. They were both strong and happy.
<|end|>


