The man smiled and said, "Yes, Tim, you can help me load the purple balloons." Tim was very happy. He helped the man load all the purple balloons onto the truck.

At the parade, Tim saw the purple balloons on a float. He felt proud that he had helped load them. Everyone cheered and had a great time at the parade. And Tim knew that he had been a part of making the parade special with the purple balloons.
