One day, a little bird named Tim was very fearful. He was scared to get food because there was a big cat near his nest. Tim's nest was high up in a tree, safe from the cat. But Tim needed to fly down to the ground to find food.

Tim's friend, a small squirrel named Sam, saw Tim was scared. Sam said, "Don't be fearful, Tim! I will help you get food." Tim was happy to have help from his friend. Together, they went down to the ground to find food.

As they were getting food, the big cat saw them. The cat tried to catch them, but Tim and Sam were too fast. They ran back up the tree and the cat could not reach them. Tim said, "Thank you, Sam! You helped me get food and saved my neck!" From that day on, they were best friends and helped each other when they were scared.
<|end|>


