Once upon a time, there was a ranch. On this ranch, there were many animals. There were cows, pigs, and chickens. The ranch was a fun place for the animals to live.

One day, a little boy named Tim came to the ranch. He saw a dull, old ball on the ground. He picked it up and said, "I want to play with this ball." So, Tim threw the ball and it went very far. But then, he could not find the ball. Tim was sad because he lost the ball.

A cow saw Tim and asked, "Why are you sad, Tim?" Tim said, "I lost my ball. It was dull and old, but I liked it." The cow said, "Do not worry, Tim. We will help you find your ball." So, all the animals on the ranch helped Tim look for his ball. They found it under a big tree. Tim was happy again, and they all played together at the ranch.
<|end|>


