"Yes, I do!" the bird replied. "I am a gifted talker. I can talk all day long. Do you like to talk too, Jane?"

Jane smiled and said, "Yes, I like to talk too! Let's be friends!" The bird and Jane talked and talked all day long. They had so much fun talking to each other. From that day on, they were the best of friends who talked every day.
