On the day of the party, Lily and Tim dressed up their toys. The icy blue car had a shiny hat, and the one-legged doll had a pretty dress. All the friends and toys gathered around. Lily and Tim said, "Now our toys are married!" Everyone clapped and cheered. The toys were happy, and Lily and Tim were best friends forever.
