Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Mia. Mia liked to wonder about the world around her. She loved to ask her mom and dad about everything she saw.

One day, Mia found a big book in her house. The book was about history. She asked her mom, "What is history?" Her mom said, "History tells us about things that happened before we were born."

Mia wanted to know more. She asked her dad, "Can you read the history book to me?" Her dad said, "This book has big words, but I can tell you a clear story about history."

Dad told Mia a story about a kind king and a brave queen from long, long ago. Mia listened and her eyes grew big. She loved the story and wanted to know more about history.

