At last, her mom went outside. Sue knew it was time to steal the sugar. She ran to the kitchen and grabbed the jar. Just as she was about to eat the sugar, her mom came back inside. "Sue! I told you not to eat the sugar!" her mom said. Sue was caught, and she knew she should have listened to her mom.
