Once upon a time, there was a pale girl named Lily. Lily liked to wear a magic hat. The magic hat was big and red. When she wore the hat, she could talk to animals. Lily loved to talk to her friends, the animals.

One day, Lily went to the woods. She wore her magic hat. She talked to the birds, the rabbits, and the squirrels. They all liked Lily very much. They played together and had fun.

But then, a big, bad wolf came. The wolf saw Lily's magic hat. He wanted the hat for himself. He took the hat from Lily. The animals could not talk to Lily anymore. The big, bad wolf wore the magic hat and scared all the animals away. Lily was very sad and missed her magic hat and her animal friends.
