The squirrel said, "I lost my nut and I worry I can't find it."

Binky wanted to help his friend. He said, "Let's organize a search to find your nut."

So, Binky and the squirrel looked all around the green forest. They looked under leaves and behind trees. At last, they found the nut under a big rock. The squirrel was very happy and thanked Binky.

