As Mia played, she heard a loud snap. She looked around and saw a big tree branch on the ground. "Oh no!" she said. Then, she heard a loud thunder sound. Mia knew that it was going to rain soon.

Mia's mom came outside and said, "Mia, we need to go inside. It's going to rain." Mia nodded and picked up her toys. They went inside and watched the rain from the window. Mia was happy to be safe and dry with her mom.
