While Tim was resting, a spoiled cat named Max came to the tree. Max wanted to play, but Tim just wanted to rest. Max was not happy. He started to climb the tree and make a lot of noise.

Tim said, "Max, please let me rest. I am very tired." Max did not listen. He kept making noise and climbing the tree. Tim's mom and dad heard the noise and came to help. They told Max to go away and let Tim rest. Max finally listened and went away.

The next day, Tim woke up feeling much better. He sang the sunrise song with his family and played with his baby sister. Tim was happy that he got to rest and his family helped him.
