Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Lily. She went to the park with her mom and saw a lost puppy.

"Mommy, can we help the puppy?" asked Lily.

"Yes, we can help the puppy. Let's take it to the safe place," replied her mom.

They took the puppy to the animal shelter where it would be available for someone to adopt. Lily was happy because she cared about the puppy and wanted it to be safe.

"Mommy, can we come back and visit the puppy?" asked Lily.

