Once upon a time, there was a little bird named Tweety. Tweety was very lonely because he didn't have any friends to play with. One day, Tweety met a little mouse named Jerry. Jerry was also lonely and looking for a friend.

Tweety and Jerry became fast friends and would play together every day. They would fly and run around, having so much fun. One day, while they were playing, Tweety blinked and accidentally hit Jerry with his wing. Jerry fell to the ground and hurt his head.

Tweety was very worried and took Jerry to see a wise owl. The owl looked at Jerry's brain and said that he would be okay, but he needed to rest for a few days. Tweety stayed with Jerry and took care of him until he was better.

From that day on, Tweety and Jerry were even closer friends. They learned that accidents can happen, but true friends are there to help each other.
