Once upon a time, there was a big ocean. It was so big, it went on and on. In the ocean, there was a little fish named Fin. Fin was a fine little fish who liked to swim and play with his friends.

One day, Fin and his friends found a big, shiny thing in the ocean. They did not know what it was, but they all wanted to take it home. Fin's best friend, Gilly, said, "Let's promise to take turns with the shiny thing." Fin and his friends all said, "We promise!"

So, Fin and his friends took turns with the shiny thing. They played with it and had lots of fun. The ocean was a happy place, and Fin and his friends were happy too. They kept their promise, and they all stayed best friends forever.
<|end|>


