Once upon a time, there was a lucky cat named Bob. Bob had a special gift. When he gave a wink, he could shrink things.

One sunny day, Bob saw his friend, a big dog named Sam. Sam was sad because he was too big to play in the little dog house. Bob had an idea. He said, "I can help you, Sam!"

Bob gave a big wink and Sam started to shrink. Now Sam was small enough to play in the little dog house. Sam was so happy and thanked Bob.

From that day on, Bob and Sam played together every day. They were the best of friends, and everyone knew how lucky they were to have each other.
<|end|>


