Once upon a time, there was a helpful boy named Tim. Tim loved to feed his pet cat, Fluffy. Every day, Tim would give Fluffy food and water. Fluffy was happy and grew big and strong.

One day, Tim and Fluffy went to the park. They saw a big muscle man lifting heavy things. "Wow," said Tim, "I want to be strong like him!" The muscle man heard Tim and said, "If you want to be strong, you must be helpful and feed your muscles with good food."

Tim listened to the muscle man and started to eat good food. He also helped his mom and dad with chores. As days went by, Tim grew stronger and stronger. One day, he saw the muscle man again. "Look at me now!" said Tim. The muscle man smiled and said, "You did it! You are strong and helpful, just like me." Tim and Fluffy were very happy.
