Once upon a time, there was a gifted bunny named Ben. Ben loved to number all the things he found in the forest. One day, he found a tunnel.

Ben hopped into the tunnel, counting as he went. One, two, three, four, five. He saw rocks, bugs, and dirt. The deeper he went, the darker it got. But Ben was brave.

At the end of the tunnel, Ben found a big, shiny rock. He knew it was special. Ben took the rock home to show his friends. They all thought Ben was the most gifted bunny in the forest.
