One day, a little girl named Lily went outside to play. The sky was blue, and the sun was shining. Lily saw a big, purple ball in her yard. She loved to play with her purple ball, so she picked it up and threw it high in the air.

As Lily played, the sky turned gray. Rain started to pour down from the clouds. Lily was sad because she did not want to stop playing. But then, something magical happened. A beautiful rainbow appeared in the sky!

Lily looked at the rainbow and saw all the pretty colors. She saw red, orange, yellow, green, blue, and purple. The rainbow made her happy, even though it was still raining. Lily danced and played in the rain with her purple ball, under the big, beautiful rainbow.
