One day, a big cat and a little dog were playing in the yard. The cat was very impatient. He wanted to play a new game. He said to the dog, "Let's play war!"

The little dog was not sure, but he wanted to make the cat happy. So, they started to play. The cat found a spray bottle and filled it with water. He said, "This is my weapon for our war!"

They took turns spraying each other with water. They laughed and ran around the yard. The little dog said, "I like this game! It's so much fun!"

In the end, they were both very wet and tired. They sat down and smiled at each other. The big cat said, "That was a great war. Let's play it again soon!" And the little dog agreed. They became best friends and played many more games together.
