Once upon a time, there was a little boy named Tim. Tim had a big, soft mattress in his room. Every night, he would lay on his mattress and imagine fun adventures.

One day, Tim imagined an icy land. The ground was cold like ice cream. He met a talking snowman who said, "Brrr, it's so icy here! Can you help me find a warm place?"

Tim thought for a moment and said, "I have an idea! Let's go to my cozy room." They went to Tim's room and the snowman sat on the big, soft mattress. The snowman felt warm and happy.

