When Tim flipped the switch, the ancient house started to shake. The folded paper shapes began to dance and fly around the room. Tim and his mom laughed and clapped their hands as they watched the paper shapes come to life.

The paper shapes danced and played with Tim and his mom all day long. When it was time for bed, Tim said, "I love our ancient house and the magic switch!" His mom smiled and said, "Me too, Tim. Sweet dreams."

