When their food arrived, Timmy's daddy took a sip of his drink and made a funny face. "This drink is yucky," he said. Timmy's mommy tasted it too and agreed. "Let's ask the waiter for something else to drink," she said.

The waiter brought them new drinks and they were much better. Timmy happily drank his milk and enjoyed his meal. From that day on, Timmy's family always asked for a taste of their drinks before they ordered them at new restaurants.
