"Don't worry, we'll help you find your mommy. What's your mommy's name?" the police officer asked. The little girl replied, "Her name is Sarah. Can you call her for me?" The police officer called Sarah and soon she arrived to pick up her little girl. Max wagged his tail happily, knowing he helped the little girl find her mommy.
