Once upon a time, there was a little bird. The bird had pretty wings and could fly very fast. One day, the bird saw a butterfly and wanted to catch it. The bird flew with great speed, but the butterfly was too quick. Suddenly, the bird felt tired and needed to rest. The bird found a tree and landed on a branch. The bird released a happy chirp and felt graceful as it rested on the branch.
<|end|>


