Once upon a time, there was a big owl named Hoot. Hoot was very graceful and could fly high up in the sky. One day, Hoot met a little mouse named Squeak. 

"Hello, little mouse. What are you doing?" asked Hoot.

"I'm looking for some cheese," replied Squeak.

"Oh, I see. Well, be careful. There are some big cats around here," warned Hoot.

Suddenly, Squeak saw a cat coming towards her. She was so scared that she started to shrink. Hoot quickly swooped down and scared the cat away. 

"Thank you, Hoot. You're my hero!" exclaimed Squeak.

"No problem, little mouse. That's what friends are for," replied Hoot with a smile.
