When they got to the kitchen, Lily's mom asked her to help mix the ingredients. But Lily accidentally spilled some on the floor. Her mom got upset and said, "Lily, you need to be careful!" Lily felt sad and started to cry.

Her mom saw how upset she was and said, "Don't worry, Lily. I'm still proud of you for trying to help. We can clean it up together." Lily felt better and they finished making the chocolate. It was the best chocolate she had ever tasted!
