One day, a little girl ran outside to feel the sun on her face. The sky was orange, like a pumpkin. 

She saw a small barn nearby and ran towards it. As she reached the barn, she heard a sound coming from inside. 

She called, "Hello? Anyone in there?"

Suddenly, a tiny rabbit jumped out and said, "Yes, it's me!" 

The little girl was so excited. She picked up the rabbit and said, "Are you ready to spring around the garden?"

The rabbit hopped up and down and said, "Yes! Let's go!"

So they sprang around the garden together, hopping and skipping, until they were both very tired. 

The little girl took the rabbit back to the barn and said goodbye. As she watched the rabbit disappear, she couldn't help but smile.
