Jill the jolly jug was strolling down the street. She felt something strange when she saw a big sign. It read, "Dead test today!"

There were lots of people around; it seemed like everyone was getting ready to take the test. Jill was feeling curious and scared at the same time. She asked a stranger why everyone was lined up for the test.

The stranger replied, "We must sign up for the test and take it before the day is over. It's very important for everyone."

Jill couldn't understand why the test was so important, but before she could ask another question, the stranger had disappeared. Taking a deep breath, Jill decided to sign up for the test.

When she finished the test, she felt a huge sense of relief. She had finally done it! She realized that the test wasn't so bad after all. Jill smiled and said goodbye to the friendly people she had met while taking the test.
