One day, Jimmy and his mommy took their dog Sparky to the veterinarian. Sparky was being very crazy, so they wanted to make sure he was okay. On the way, Jimmy asked his mommy what the veterinarian would do. Mommy said that the veterinarian would prepare Sparky and make sure he was healthy.

When they got to the vet, Jimmy was a little scared of the doctor. But Mommy told him that the doctor was nice and that Sparky was in good hands. The veterinarian prepared a big exam for Sparky. She carefully listened to his heart and checked his fur. She also gave Sparky a couple of different medicines.

When the veterinarian was finished preparing Sparky, she said he was very healthy. She even gave Jimmy a special treat for being so brave. Jimmy was so happy that Sparky was feeling better. He thanked the veterinarian for taking such great care of his dog. Sparky and Jimmy then made their way back home, happy and healthy.
