Grace said impatiently, "Mummy, I'm so hungry. Can I have something to eat?"

Mummy replied, "Yes, Grace. But you must eat all your lunch first. Only then can you have a special treat!"

Grace was so excited. She quickly ate all her lunch and waited impatiently for her special treat. When Mummy came back she had a big smile on her face. In her hands was a colourful spinning top.

Grace was so happy! She quickly started to spin the top across the floor and she laughed with joy. 

Grace enjoyed spinning all afternoon, feeling content and full in her tummy.
