It was a hot day, and Meg was outside with her pet rabbit named Mop. Meg was running and chasing Mop around the garden. She giggled as Mop hopped and jumped around the grass. Suddenly, Meg noticed something in the distance. A storm cloud was rolling in, quickly and silently. She rushed to Mop and scooped him up with her arms. 

