"My name is Froggie," he said. "Did you come here to polish your jeep?"

The man smiled.

"Yes, I came here to polish it every day," he said.

Froggie hopped out of the car.

"I want to help," he said excitedly.

The man gave Froggie a soft cloth and showed him how to polish the jeep. They polished until the jeep was so shiny it almost blinded them.

