Once upon a time there lived a loyal cop called Blue. Blue worked in a big city where there were always bad things happening. One day, Blue was on duty when he seen a naughty car zipping away down the street. He knew it was up to him to catch it.

Blue zipped off after the car on his motorbike. He worked hard to keep up with the car, but it was going too fast. Suddenly, Blue's motorbike started to splutter and eventually it stopped working!

Blue got off his bike and shouted out to the car "stop!" But the car just kept zipping away. Blue felt so frustrated, but he was loyal to his job so he started running after the car.

Eventually, the car began to slow down and Blue caught the driver. He put the driver in handcuffs and took him to the police station. Blue had done his job and he felt very brave and loyal.
<|end|>


