Once there was a tiger named Tim. He was big and fat. He liked to eat a lot of food.

One day, Tim was walking in the forest. He wanted to find some food. It was then that he saw a change.

The change was a big rat! Tim was scared so he stood still as the rat crossed his path. Suddenly, he heard a voice.

"Hello Tim," said the rat. "I'm here to tell you something."

"What is it?" asked Tim.

"You will change," said the rat.

Tim was confused. "What do you mean?"

"You will become bigger and fat like me," said the rat.

Tim smiled. He liked the idea of being bigger and fat.

From that day forward, Tim started to eat more and more. He became bigger and fatter. He was happy and content. His friends all said he looked like a real tiger now.
