Mary stopped playing and looked at the man. She smiled and said, "This silly game is teaching me an important lesson. It's teaching me that life is all about balance."

The man was surprised to hear these wise words come from Mary's mouth. He nodded his head and said, "You are absolutely right. Thank you for this valuable lesson."

When Mary left the park, she felt like she had learned an important lesson. Balance is essential in life to stay happy.
