Once upon a time, there was a deep cat. Its name was Jimmy. Jimmy was always looking for friends, but none of the other cats accepted him. One day, Jimmy was walking through the woods, feeling very sad and lonely when he heard a voice. 

"Hey! You don't look so happy," the voice said.

Jimmy looked around, and saw a little girl wearing a pink dress.

"My name is Lucy," the girl said. "I noticed you looking unhappy, so I wanted to say hello."

Jimmy was amazed! He'd never had someone accept him before.

"Thank you!" He said.

From then on, Jimmy and Lucy were the best of friends. They played together in the woods every day, and Jimmy was so pleased to have a friend who accepted him for who he was.
<|end|>


