Dave asked the driver, "Please sir, can you help me? I really want to go to the park."

The driver smiled at him and said, "I'm sorry, little fella. We aren't going that way. But if you wait here, I'm sure you will find someone who can help you."

Dave looked around at the other passengers, but everyone was busy talking. He wasn't sure what to do. Suddenly, the driver shouted, "You can manage it, Dave! Get off the bus, look for signs and you will find your way."

Dave took the driver's advice and got off the bus. He looked around and spotted a sign with a picture of a park. He thanked the driver and ran off with an enthusiastic smile on his face. He easily managed to find the park and had a great time there.
<|end|>


