Once upon a time, there was a little girl named Katie. She was only three years old, but she was very adventurous. 

One day, Katie was exploring in her backyard when she noticed something mysterious. "What is that?" she said as she looked at the little knob in the ground. 

Katie's mom heard her and came running over. 

"It looks like someone has buried something here, Katie," her mom said. "Let's bring it inside and see what it is." 

So Katie's mom carefully dug the knob out of the ground and brought it inside. Katie jumped up and down with excitement! 

Once inside, Katie and her mom brushed the dirt off the knob and unscrewed it. To their surprise, inside was a secret note! 

Katie's mom read the note aloud. It said: "Today is a very mysterious day, find the treasures and let the fun come your way!" 

Katie and her mom laughed and clapped their hands. It was going to be an exciting day!
