One day, Jimmy went outside to play. He saw a delicate, white kitten zoom by. He wanted to pet it, so he chased it. When he reached the kitten, he found it hiding in a bush. He tried to get it out, but the kitten hissed and ran away.

Jimmy was sad that he couldn't pet the kitten. His mom came by and said, "Don't worry, Jimmy. Maybe if you're patient, you'll get to pet the kitten." 

The next day, Jimmy decided to try again. He went outside and waited patiently on the porch. Suddenly, he saw the delicate white kitten zoom by. This time, the kitten stopped and approached him.

Jimmy was so excited. He stroked the kitten's soft fur and whispered gently to it. Just then, the delicate white kitten purred and rubbed against him. Jimmy had finally made a new friend!
