Tommy was walking down the street one night with his mom and dad. He was very excited to see the puppies in the pet shop. As they walked, Tommy noticed something strange in the road. It was a big shadow. He stopped and stared at it.

Tommy's dad put his arms around Tommy, and they watched the shadow together. Then Tommy noticed something behind them. There were two little puppies in the pet shop window, and they were both so adorable. They were staring back at Tommy and his family.

