Once there was a robot named Tini. He was a very quiet robot. He lived in a bright and colorful house and he was always happy.

One day, Tini saw an amazing thing outside the window. It was a car! It was going so fast!

Tini asked his mom: "Mom, what's that?"

Mom answered: "That is a car, Tini. It's speeding!"

Tini was so excited. He wanted to be like the car and speed too. So he asked his mom: "Can I speed too, mom?"

His mom said: "No, Tini. Robots can't speed. But you can be a very quiet robot. Is that okay?"

And Tini said, "Yes, mom! I can be a quiet robot!"
